#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "Profane Curse"
msgstr "亵渎诅咒"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Profane Curse'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid ""
"A curse lingers through your body, amplifying elemental damage you take."
msgstr "一道诅咒在你体内萦绕，放大了你受到的元素伤害。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Profane Curse'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "You've been cursed."
msgstr "你已被诅咒。"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Profane Curse'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "You feel your body thaw from the curse."
msgstr "你感到身体从诅咒中解冻。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "Conceal"
msgstr "隐匿"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Conceal'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "Your body is invisible to the naked eye."
msgstr "你的身体对肉眼不可见。"

#. ~ Apply message for effect(s) 'Conceal'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "You've turned invisible!"
msgstr "你已隐身！"

#. ~ Remove message for effect(s) 'Conceal'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_effects.json
msgid "You reveal yourself."
msgstr "你显形了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Sacrifice"
msgstr "献祭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Sacrifice'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Instant death damage is dealt."
msgstr "造成了即死伤害。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Teleport"
msgstr "传送"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Teleport'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Concealment'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Combined with blind strike spell."
msgstr "与盲击法术结合。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Concealment"
msgstr "隐匿状态"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Blind Strike"
msgstr "盲击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blind Strike'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid ""
"Caster teleports and quickly strikes the target, dealing moderate cutting "
"damage, then turns invisible while retreating to a random spot."
msgstr "施法者传送并快速攻击目标，造成中等切割伤害，随后在撤退到随机位置时隐身。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Innate Strike"
msgstr "本能打击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Innate Strike'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "A quick surge of mana blast strikes the target, dealing bash damage."
msgstr "一股快速的魔力冲击击中目标，造成钝击伤害。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Stun"
msgstr "眩晕"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Stun'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid ""
"Caster channels its mind to its target, eventually renders them unconscious "
"for a few turns."
msgstr "施法者将意念传导至目标，最终使其昏迷数回合。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Dark Fireblast"
msgstr "暗黑炎爆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dark Fireblast'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid ""
"Fire infused with black magic engulfs the target, inflicting them with "
"profane curse."
msgstr "蕴含黑魔法的火焰吞噬目标，使其遭受亵渎诅咒。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T7.json
msgid "Desecrate"
msgstr "亵渎"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Desecrate'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid ""
"Caster channels the underworld for a very long time to desecrate the targets"
" with pillars of hellish flames."
msgstr "施法者长时间引导冥界之力，以地狱火柱亵渎目标。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Heal"
msgstr "治疗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Heal'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Combined with transfusion spell."
msgstr "与输血法术结合。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T1.json
msgid "Transfusion"
msgstr "输血"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Transfusion'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Drains life force from the target, may be it an ally or a foe."
msgstr "从目标身上汲取生命力，无论其是友军还是敌人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Blood Ripple"
msgstr "血波"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Ripple'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Combined with blood surge spell."
msgstr "与血液涌动法术结合。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T4.json
msgid "Blood Surge"
msgstr "血液涌动"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Surge'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid ""
"A wave of blood is drawn out from the caster, dealing bio damage to the main"
" target and bash to the surrounding targets."
msgstr "一股血浪从施法者体内涌出，对主要目标造成生化伤害，并对周围目标造成冲击。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Share"
msgstr "共享"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Share'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid ""
"Caster sends out blood tentacles that attaches to nearby allies, regaining "
"large portion of health while damaging the caster."
msgstr "施法者释放血触手连接附近盟友，恢复大量生命值，同时伤害施法者自身。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Share Blood"
msgstr "共享血液"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Share Blood'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\monster_magic.json
msgid "Combined with share spell."
msgstr "与共享法术结合。"

