#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid "bat"
msgid_plural "bats"
msgstr[0] "蝙蝠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid ""
"One of the vesper bats, a family of winged insect-eating mammals.  It roosts"
" in caves and other hollows, and uses a form of echolocation to aerially "
"navigate through tricky terrain at rapid speeds."
msgstr "属于暮蝠科的一种，这类有翼食虫哺乳动物栖息于洞穴及其他空洞中，利用回声定位在复杂地形中高速飞行导航。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vampire bat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid ""
"A mammalian creature commonly found at caverns and thick foliage. It has "
"grown in fondness with the dark, and capable in terrain echolocation."
msgstr "一种常见于洞穴与茂密植被中的哺乳动物。它已逐渐适应黑暗环境，并具备地形回声定位能力。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid "large vampire bat"
msgid_plural "large vampire bats"
msgstr[0] "大型吸血蝠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'large vampire bat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid ""
"A larger vampire bat, with longer wingspan and visible fangs. Shows "
"aggression when startled, and detects them with screeching sounds they make."
msgstr "一种体型更大的吸血蝠，翼展更长且獠牙外露。受惊时会显露出攻击性，并通过发出的尖啸声探测目标。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid "feral vampire bat"
msgid_plural "feral vampire bats"
msgstr[0] "野化吸血蝠"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'feral vampire bat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Critters\Bats.json
msgid ""
"A large vampire bat - with seeping bubbly liquid in its mouth - engorged to "
"attack whatever is detected."
msgstr "一种大型吸血蝠——口中渗出泡沫状液体——膨胀着准备攻击任何被探测到的目标。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "abominable leech"
msgid_plural "abominable leechs"
msgstr[0] "憎恶蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'abominable leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A leech with green and yellow segmented colors, it drips concentrated toxin "
"as it slither along the way."
msgstr "一种带有黄绿相间环节颜色的蛭虫，爬行时会滴落浓缩毒素。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "acidic leech"
msgid_plural "acidic leechs"
msgstr[0] "酸蚀蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'acidic leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"Its mouth doesn't stop drooping yellowish chemical stuff into the terrain it"
" passes by. This leech's flesh has completely adopted to handle the extreme "
"hazards cause by acid, and became a part to its internal organs. Due to "
"thinned skin layer, it is fragile to physical harm, but overprotected by "
"burning blood."
msgstr ""
"它的口器不断向途经的地面滴落黄色化学物质。这种蛭的肉体已完全适应酸性极端危害，并成为其内脏器官的一部分。由于皮肤层变薄，它对物理伤害很脆弱，但被炽热血液过度保护着。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "big leech"
msgid_plural "big leechs"
msgstr[0] "巨蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'big leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A larger, segmented worm. The bite it makes can suck out liters of blood if "
"remains intact for minutes."
msgstr "一种体型更大、分节的蠕虫。如果其咬伤保持完整数分钟，可吸出数升血液。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "bloated leech"
msgid_plural "bloated leechs"
msgstr[0] "肿胀水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloated leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A large worm with a nearly transparent, bloated hump in its back, filled "
"with pressurized poison gas. It slithers faster than most and definitely, it"
" will explode when touched."
msgstr "一种大型蠕虫，背部有一个近乎透明、肿胀的隆起，内部充满加压的毒气。它比大多数同类蠕动得更快，且一旦被触碰就必定会爆炸。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "devourer leech"
msgid_plural "devourer leechs"
msgstr[0] "吞噬水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'devourer leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"It excrete blood from its body continuously as it slithers very slow. This "
"enormous leech has hundreds of teeth and slabs of elastic skin makes it "
"hideous physically."
msgstr "它在极其缓慢的蠕动过程中持续从体内排出血液。这只巨大的水蛭拥有数百颗牙齿，大块弹性皮肤使其外形骇人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "blood surge leech"
msgid_plural "blood surge leechs"
msgstr[0] "血涌水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood surge leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A man-sized, monoeye leech with a bubbling blood residue under its mouth and"
" a saggy skin lies under it. If left unnoticed, it can shoot with pressurize"
" power!"
msgstr "一种人形大小的单眼水蛭，口部下方有冒泡的血渍和松弛的皮肤。若未被察觉，它能以加压力量喷射攻击！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "The blood surge leech showers its blood!"
msgstr "血涌水蛭喷洒出它的血液！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "dreadful leech"
msgid_plural "dreadful leechs"
msgstr[0] "恐怖水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'dreadful leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A leech with devilish, blade fangs potruding from its mouth. Its thirst for "
"vampire blood caused it to mutate to even more dreadful look, and even more "
"troubles!"
msgstr "一种口中突出恶魔般刃状尖牙的水蛭。对吸血鬼血液的渴望使其变异成更恐怖的外形，也带来更多麻烦！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "eyed leech"
msgid_plural "eyed leechs"
msgstr[0] "独眼水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'eyed leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A small leech with a distinctive large, monoeye above its mouth. Being "
"compatible to precisely shoot its own teeth makes it deadly once ignored."
msgstr "一种小型水蛭，口部上方有独特的大型单眼。能够精准喷射自身牙齿的特性使其一旦被忽视便极为致命。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "The eyed leech spew its tooth!"
msgstr "独眼水蛭喷射出它的牙齿！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "huge leech"
msgid_plural "huge leechs"
msgstr[0] "巨型水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'huge leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"While it lives, the vastly accumulated blood it has sucked from anything has"
" changed its appearance. This human sized parasite doesn't drink blood "
"anymore... They are eaten as whole instead. Aside that, its hide can deflect"
" almost any inferior projectiles."
msgstr ""
"存活期间，它从万物身上吸取的大量血液改变了其外貌。这种人类体型的寄生虫不再饮血……而是直接吞食整体。此外，它的外皮能偏转几乎所有低级投射物。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A segmented, small worm technically a pest for living things. When biting, "
"it extracts a liquid from its mouth that disables blood clotting, which can "
"be deadly for a limited time."
msgstr "一种分节的小型蠕虫，实为生物害虫。咬伤时，它会从口中分泌一种液体阻止血液凝固，短时间内可能致命。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "sharpshooter leech"
msgid_plural "sharpshooter leechs"
msgstr[0] "神射手水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'sharpshooter leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"Small, but deadly! The mutation in its iris has changed its presicion and "
"shoots further with sharper teeth ammunition inside its mouth."
msgstr "体型虽小，却致命无比！其虹膜的变异提升了精准度，能以口中更锋利的牙齿弹药射击更远距离。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "The sharpshooter leech spew it tooth!"
msgstr "神射手水蛭喷射出它的牙齿！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "spiky leech"
msgid_plural "spiky leechs"
msgstr[0] "尖刺水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'spiky leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"This overgrown leech possesses tremendous amount of short bone spikes "
"overlapping around its flabby skin. Much slower, tougher and deadlier than "
"before."
msgstr "这只过度生长的水蛭拥有大量短骨刺，重叠覆盖在其松弛的皮肤上。比以往更慢、更坚韧、更致命。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "vampire leech"
msgid_plural "vampire leechs"
msgstr[0] "吸血鬼水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'vampire leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"This large leech somehow gained a power from a vampire blood, and caused it "
"to mutate a longer teeth lining. The sucking power that it does will drain "
"you in a pinch."
msgstr "这只大型水蛭不知何故从吸血鬼血液中获得了力量，导致其变异出更长的牙齿排列。其吸血能力会在瞬间将你榨干。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid "venomous leech"
msgid_plural "venomous leechs"
msgstr[0] "剧毒水蛭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'venomous leech'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Insects\+Leech.json
msgid ""
"A larger, darker abominable leech with wider mouth and drips highly "
"concentrated toxin as it sway."
msgstr "一只更大、更暗的可憎水蛭，嘴巴更宽，摇摆时滴下高浓度毒素。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid "blood compact zombie"
msgid_plural "blood compact zombies"
msgstr[0] "血凝僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood compact zombie'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid ""
"From the old graveyard it arised. This zombie's age cause its blood to "
"solidify into thick, rock-like armor, but somehow maintains natural speed. "
"With odd-looking teeth lining and stony claws, its threat is impeccable."
msgstr ""
"它从古老的墓地中崛起。这只僵尸的年龄使其血液凝固成厚重的岩石般护甲，但不知何故保持了自然速度。拥有奇特的牙齿排列和石质利爪，其威胁无可挑剔。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid "blood defused zombie"
msgid_plural "blood defused zombies"
msgstr[0] "血散僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood defused zombie'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid ""
"This hollowed zombie's blood melts away and cause a minor mutation, such as "
"long claws and immensive fangs. Lackness of weight provides swiftness and "
"good reflexes, but in most cases, its fragility makes it easy to take down."
msgstr "这只空洞僵尸的血液融化并导致轻微变异，例如长爪和巨大尖牙。重量缺失提供了迅捷和良好反射，但在大多数情况下，其脆弱性使其容易被击倒。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid "blood infused zombie"
msgid_plural "blood infused zombies"
msgstr[0] "血注僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood infused zombie'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid ""
"Once a compact zombie, but its blood has soaked and caused to mutate into a "
"dangerous oversized bone plates and spikes, leaving its fleshy skin saggy. "
"The bone scythes on its hands are symmetrical as a pair while its sharpened "
"teeth potrudes from its jaw, but despite fearsome looks, its weight causes "
"it to stumble... often."
msgstr ""
"曾是血凝僵尸，但其血液浸透并导致变异成危险的超大骨板和骨刺，使其肉质皮肤松弛下垂。手上的骨镰对称成对，而锋利的牙齿从颚部突出，但尽管外表可怖，其重量常导致它步履蹒跚。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid "bone titan zombie"
msgid_plural "bone titan zombies"
msgstr[0] "骨泰坦僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bone titan zombie'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid ""
"An enlarged skeleton mutant with extremely thick bone platings around its "
"body. It walks slowly from carrying itself up."
msgstr "一只放大的骨架突变体，身体周围覆盖着极厚的骨板。因负重而缓慢行走。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid "bone wraith zombie"
msgid_plural "bone wraith zombies"
msgstr[0] "骨幽灵僵尸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bone wraith zombie'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Graveyard.json
msgid ""
"A skeleton mutant with symmetrical slender thin bone growths on its back, "
"similar to spider's, but appears to be unused in its movement. Being almost "
"weightless, it is quick and lethal alone."
msgstr "一只骨架突变体，背部对称生长着细长的薄骨结构，类似蜘蛛，但似乎在其移动中未被使用。几乎无重量，单独行动时迅捷而致命。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid "succumbed vampire"
msgid_plural "succumbed vampires"
msgstr[0] "沉沦吸血鬼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'succumbed vampire'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid ""
"This glorious entity has been engulfed by black, oozing liquid on its eye. "
"Still walks in passion, its thirst for blood has been replaced with fresh "
"meat."
msgstr "这个辉煌实体已被黑色渗出液体吞噬了眼睛。仍以激情行走，其对鲜血的渴望已被新鲜血肉取代。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid "rogue sinker"
msgid_plural "rogue sinkers"
msgstr[0] "游荡沉沦者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'rogue sinker'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid ""
"Shrouded in black, mystical mist, it moves silently in every step while "
"remains unseen to its prey. A vampire skilled in lashing and striking, with "
"pure wisdom to the acts of the dark days."
msgstr "笼罩在黑色神秘雾气中，它每一步都悄无声息地移动，同时对其猎物保持隐形。一只擅长抽打和突袭的吸血鬼，对黑暗时代的行为了如指掌。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid "wicked warlock"
msgid_plural "wicked warlocks"
msgstr[0] "邪恶术士"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'wicked warlock'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid ""
"A vampire full of malice, with hands twitching as if it holds knowledge to "
"spellcrafts. Eyes fallen in deep void, it simply expresses frightful desires"
" among the living."
msgstr "一个充满恶意的吸血鬼，双手抽搐仿佛掌握着咒术知识。双眼深陷虚无，仅向生者表达着可怖的欲望。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid "profane conjurer"
msgid_plural "profane conjurers"
msgstr[0] "亵渎召唤师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'profane conjurer'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid ""
"A dark cultist, lays low in its deceiving blank appearance. Hands swaying "
"slyly, it occasionally pulses in black aura, denoting a strong familiarity "
"with ancient profane arts."
msgstr "一名黑暗邪教徒，以欺骗性的空白外表潜伏。双手狡黠地摆动，偶尔泛起黑色灵光，显示出对古老亵渎之术的深刻熟悉。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid "hemomancer"
msgid_plural "hemomancers"
msgstr[0] "血法师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'hemomancer'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Monsters\Zombies\Vampire.json
msgid ""
"Frantic, but skillful to the arts of hemomancy - one of the oldest form of "
"sorcery. A vampire that drains and manipulates life from creatures within "
"its vicinity to conjure intricate spells."
msgstr "狂热却精于血魔法——最古老的巫术形式之一。这种吸血鬼汲取并操控周围生物的生命力，以施展精妙的法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_classes.json
msgid "Warlock"
msgstr "术士"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Warlock'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_classes.json
msgid ""
"Warlocks follow the rules of the ancient chaotic idols, idols that were said"
" to lived before the existence of the world. They are also called as dark "
"magus, known for their destructive influence over magic. Though it is from "
"the depths of history, their potency remains immeasurable."
msgstr ""
"术士遵循古老混沌神祇的法则，这些神祇据说在世界存在之前就已存在。他们也被称为黑暗法师，以其对魔法的毁灭性影响力而闻名。尽管源自历史深处，他们的力量依然不可估量。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_classes.json
msgid "Profane Conjurer"
msgstr "亵渎召唤师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Profane Conjurer'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_classes.json
msgid ""
"Profane conjurers reside far from the world, harnessing the dark elements "
"and take control for their own desires. Their magic is imbued with pure "
"evil, infused with elements lead to the corruption of the weak."
msgstr "亵渎召唤师远离尘世，驾驭黑暗元素并为其欲望所控。他们的魔法浸透着纯粹的邪恶，蕴含导致弱者腐化的元素。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_classes.json
msgid "Hemomancer"
msgstr "血法师"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Hemomancer'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_classes.json
msgid ""
"Hemomancers tend to be resourceful in their environment, manipulating the "
"life force of one's self and seize other's to bind for their own will. They "
"risk their lives in order to overwhelm those who opposes."
msgstr "血法师善于利用环境，操控自身生命力并夺取他人生命以束缚其意志。他们冒着生命危险以压制反对者。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_dialogue_traits.json
msgid "Mark of the Vampire"
msgstr "吸血鬼印记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mark of the Vampire'}
#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mark of the Human'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_dialogue_traits.json
msgid "NPCs will check your progress with this trait."
msgstr "NPC会检查你在此特质上的进展。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_dialogue_traits.json
msgid "Mark of the Human"
msgstr "人类印记"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_dialogue_traits.json
msgid "Survivor Story"
msgstr "幸存者故事"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Survivor Story'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_dialogue_traits.json
msgid "NPC with this trait tells their unique story."
msgstr "拥有此特质的NPC会讲述他们独特的故事。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_mutation.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Vampire"
msgstr "吸血鬼"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vampire'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Mutation\v_mutation.json
msgid ""
"Your proof of immortality. You invested your whole life on a countless "
"battles with immensive power and all of your experiences has paid off until "
"now. The living nightmare of the dark days, is now a scavenger of Cataclysm."
msgstr "你不朽的证明。你将一生投入无数战斗，拥有强大力量，所有经验至今已得回报。黑暗时代的活梦魇，如今是灾变的拾荒者。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Isolated vampires."
msgstr "孤立的吸血鬼。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Underground Vampires"
msgstr "地下吸血鬼"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Underground vampire refugees."
msgstr "地下吸血鬼难民。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Underground vampire traders."
msgstr "地下吸血鬼商人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Underground vampire commando."
msgstr "地下吸血鬼突击队员。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Wasteland Vampires"
msgstr "废土吸血鬼"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Wasteland refugees."
msgstr "废土难民。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Wasteland Guard Vampire"
msgstr "废土守卫吸血鬼"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Wasteland refugee guard."
msgstr "废土难民守卫。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Vampire Gunkeeper"
msgstr "吸血鬼枪械保管员"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Gunshop owner."
msgstr "枪店店主。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Wasteland Refugee"
msgstr "废土难民"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "I hide at wastelands."
msgstr "我藏身于废土之中。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "Shopkeep"
msgstr "店主"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_classes.json
msgid "I trade at wastelands."
msgstr "我在废土进行交易。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_faction.json
msgid "Vampires"
msgstr "吸血鬼"

#. ~ Description for Vampires
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_faction.json
msgid ""
"A malicious group of inhumane entities that thrives to live in peace, and "
"tends to help the last surviving humans. They do not come in sizes, but "
"their dark century experiences are beyond expectations. Their purpose is to "
"hope for humans to survive and assists to eradicate anything threatens them "
"with their utmost capabilities."
msgstr ""
"一个恶意的非人实体群体，致力于和平生活，并倾向于帮助最后幸存的人类。他们体型各异，但其黑暗世纪的经验远超预期。他们的目的是希望人类生存，并竭尽全力协助消除任何威胁。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_faction.json
msgid "Wasteland Dwellers"
msgstr "废土居民"

#. ~ Description for Wasteland Dwellers
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_faction.json
msgid ""
"A community of people who resides at the wasteland outskirts. They seek "
"refuge from unnatural hazards, and has chosen to live with vampires. Unsure "
"about its consequences, but still are trustworthy towards them."
msgstr "一群居住在废土边缘地带的人们。他们寻求躲避非自然危害的庇护，并选择与吸血鬼共同生活。虽不确定其后果，但仍对他们保持信任。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Underguard"
msgstr "地下守卫"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Trader"
msgstr "商人"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Commando"
msgstr "突击队员"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Gunshop Owner"
msgstr "枪店店主"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Wasteguard"
msgstr "废土守卫"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Junkshop Owner"
msgstr "废品店老板"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Refugee"
msgstr "难民"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Radio Specialist"
msgstr "无线电专家"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc.json
msgid "Prisoner"
msgstr "囚犯"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Collect 30 blood"
msgstr "收集30份血液"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Collect 30 blood'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Collect <color_light_red>30 human blood</color> then bring it to the "
"commando."
msgstr "收集<color_light_red>30份人类血液</color>然后带给突击队员。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This errand needs you."
msgstr "这个差事需要你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Blood... Our main food for darkest centuries. Even I almost forgot its "
"taste, I'd like to drink it again. Bring me 30, too much but it is essential"
" in many ways."
msgstr "血液……我们黑暗世纪的主要食物。即便我几乎忘了它的味道，我还是想再尝一次。给我带30份来，虽然很多，但它在很多方面都必不可少。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Okay, descendant. This won't be hard and take your time."
msgstr "好的，后裔。这不会很难，慢慢来。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "If only you let me shoot your chest, this will be done easily."
msgstr "只要你让我射穿你的胸膛，这事就能轻松搞定。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "."
msgstr "。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Drinks? You have the drinks ready?"
msgstr "饮料？你准备好饮料了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "These blood certainly are useful. Thanks for this treats, descendant."
msgstr "这些血液确实有用。谢谢你的款待，后裔。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, thank you. *smirks*"
msgstr "嗯，谢谢你。*得意地笑*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*grins*"
msgstr "*咧嘴笑*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Collect 15 small leech teeth"
msgstr "收集15颗小型水蛭牙齿"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Collect 15 small leech teeth'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Gather <color_light_red>15 small leech teeth</color> and give them to the "
"commando. They are rarely dropped by <color_magenta>leeches</color> that "
"lives in the <color_light_blue>swamp</color>."
msgstr ""
"收集<color_light_red>15颗小型水蛭牙齿</color>并交给突击队员。它们由生活在<color_light_blue>沼泽</color>中的<color_magenta>水蛭</color>稀有掉落。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I want you to slay something..."
msgstr "我要你去猎杀一些东西……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Ofcourse you know about the bloodsucking pests on the swamp, we hate those "
"parasites squirming for blood to live. Hand over 15 of their teeth as a "
"proof to succeed this trial."
msgstr "你当然知道沼泽里那些吸血的害虫，我们讨厌那些为了生存而蠕动吸血的寄生虫。交出15颗它们的牙齿作为完成这次试炼的证明。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Slay them in any way you want."
msgstr "用任何你想要的方式猎杀它们。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "It's just okay."
msgstr "这还行。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "They are blind, and depends on what they hear or smell."
msgstr "它们是盲的，依赖听觉或嗅觉。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Got 'em?"
msgstr "搞定了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Nice work, I guess they won't bother us for a long time."
msgstr "干得漂亮，我想它们很长一段时间都不会来烦我们了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*slurping*"
msgstr "*吸溜声*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Take blood sac from the giant \"Thing\""
msgstr "从巨型“怪物”身上取得血囊"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Take blood sac from the giant
#. "Thing"'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Get the <color_light_red>blood sac</color> by slaying the <color_magenta>giant \"Thing\"</color>, then deliver it to the commando.\n"
"<color_red>Going unprepared is a death trap!</color>."
msgstr ""
"通过击杀<color_magenta>巨型“怪物”</color>来获取<color_light_red>血囊</color>，然后将其交给突击队员。\n"
"<color_red>毫无准备就去就是自寻死路！</color>"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is pretty much risky to you... Going to do it?"
msgstr "这对你来说相当危险……你确定要去做吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"There is a peculiar cave with vast blood residue in it and I think its their"
" gathering place. This giant \"thing\" on the depths, you'll need to bring "
"it down as my command."
msgstr "有一个特殊的洞穴，里面残留着大量血迹，我认为那是它们的聚集地。在深处的那只巨型“怪物”，你需要按照我的命令将其消灭。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Bring its blood sac, that would be a nice prize taking it down and as a "
"proof of succeeding this test."
msgstr "带回它的血囊，这将是消灭它的不错奖励，也是完成这项考验的证明。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Gather your courage first."
msgstr "先鼓起你的勇气。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"It is blind and very slow, slower than a human snail, but it'll devour you "
"and causes deadly injuries getting near it... Now get going!"
msgstr "它是盲的，而且行动非常缓慢，比蜗牛还慢，但一旦靠近它，它会吞噬你并造成致命伤害……现在出发吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Killed it?"
msgstr "干掉它了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Damn kid, that's the mess you wanted to get. And you are still alive after "
"that!"
msgstr "该死的小子，这就是你想惹的麻烦。而且你居然还活着！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Ummm... I want to shoot you."
msgstr "嗯……我想给你一枪。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Kill 200 zombies"
msgstr "击杀200个僵尸"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Kill 200 zombies'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Kill <color_light_red>200 zombies</color> then talk to the commando after "
"completion."
msgstr "击杀<color_light_red>200个僵尸</color>，完成后与突击队员交谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is the final test I can give you... Still want to try?"
msgstr "这是我能给你的最终考验……还想试试吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I've heard that these \"blobs\" was the cause of all troubles and horrifying"
" events worldwide. As my command, eliminate 200 of these walking corpses to "
"succeed... Later on, I will tell you something after this."
msgstr "我听说这些“烂肉”是全球所有麻烦和恐怖事件的根源。按照我的命令，消灭200具这些行走的尸体以通过考验……之后，我会告诉你一些事情。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Prepare yourself before jumping into this mess."
msgstr "在卷入这场混乱之前，先做好准备。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just prepare yourself for this job."
msgstr "为这份工作做好准备就行。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Visit some heavily crowded areas."
msgstr "探访一些人流密集的区域。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "How is the hunt going?"
msgstr "狩猎进行得如何了？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Hmm... HE appreciates your doings, my comrade. I thank you for your "
"assistance and giving your precious time dealing with these requests I have "
"made for you..."
msgstr "嗯……祂很欣赏你的作为，我的同志。感谢你的协助，并花费宝贵时间处理我为你提出的这些请求……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What good does this do us?"
msgstr "这对我们有什么好处？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "It was a lost cause anyways..."
msgstr "反正这本来就是无望之事……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Collect 15 blood"
msgstr "收集15份血液"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Collect 15 blood'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Gather <color_light_red>15 human blood</color> then bring it to the vampire."
msgstr "收集<color_light_red>15份人类血液</color>，然后带给吸血鬼。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I want you for this errand."
msgstr "我想让你跑这趟差事。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Did you know we have been using blood substitutes for decades? Well, that's "
"a good thing for us. Now, I want you to collect a few human blood, either "
"yours or not... 15, I suppose that will satisfy my pleasure for that taste "
"once again."
msgstr ""
"你知道吗，我们使用血液替代品已经几十年了？嗯，这对我们来说是件好事。现在，我想让你收集一些人类血液，不管是不是你自己的……15份，我想这能让我再次满足于那种滋味。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"You better do this. Sinking my fangs onto your flimsy neck is indeed fatal."
msgstr "你最好照做。把我的尖牙刺进你那脆弱的脖子确实是致命的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Talk to me again later if you want to help me."
msgstr "如果你想帮我，晚点再来找我。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Murder someone if you are desperate to collect them."
msgstr "如果你急于收集它们，就去杀个人吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Did you get my drinks?"
msgstr "你拿到我的饮料了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Fascinating work, mortal."
msgstr "干得漂亮，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*smilesatyou*"
msgstr "*对你微笑*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Take down 10 elder zombies"
msgstr "消灭10个年长僵尸"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Take down 10 elder zombies'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Slay <color_magenta>10 elder zombies</color> then talk to the vampire after "
"completion.  <color_magenta>Elder zombies</color> are depicted to their "
"stone-like, compact blood and are rarely seen in the "
"<color_light_blue>graveyards</color>."
msgstr ""
"击杀<color_magenta>10个年长僵尸</color>，完成后与吸血鬼交谈。<color_magenta>年长僵尸</color>的特征是它们如石头般、凝结的血液，在<color_light_blue>墓地</color>中较为罕见。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is a little harder..."
msgstr "这个稍微难一点……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"The gravestone in this crypt were built long ago, and the dead bodies has "
"been buried here since before I reside here. Surprisingly, they were "
"resurrected with this odd \"magic\". I want you to take 10 of them down and "
"let their hollow vessel for an eternal rest."
msgstr ""
"这座墓穴中的墓碑建于很久以前，尸体在我居住于此之前就已埋葬于此。令人惊讶的是，它们被这种奇怪的“魔法”复活了。我要你消灭其中10个，让它们空洞的躯壳得以安息。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good. Now go outside and look for them."
msgstr "很好。现在出去找它们吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Come back later."
msgstr "晚点再来。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Their blood has calcified into a shell, and it is distinctive to their "
"appearance."
msgstr "它们的血液已钙化成外壳，这是它们外观的显著特征。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Now?"
msgstr "现在？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I know you can do it..."
msgstr "我知道你能做到的……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*glares*"
msgstr "*怒视*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bring a bloodrune"
msgstr "带一个血符文来"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Bring a bloodrune'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Get a <color_light_red>bloodrune</color> then deliver it to the vampire."
msgstr "获取一个<color_light_red>血符文</color>，然后交给吸血鬼。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is a bit hard for you. You still want to try?"
msgstr "这对你来说有点难。你还想试试吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Bloodrune... The vampire's eternal soul. Merely a fact that few of us night creatures turn into an object upon death, yet most resists to that point.\n"
"In the dark days, bloodrunes are set in a pedestal by elder civilizations, and said that their \"god\" will accept it as a praise, which is not true. Get this rune for me, to honor its soul in a way we normally do."
msgstr ""
"血符文……吸血鬼的不朽灵魂。事实是，我们夜行生物中只有少数在死亡时会化为物体，而大多数则抗拒到那一刻。\n"
"在黑暗年代，古老文明将血符文置于基座上，声称他们的“神”会接受其为赞颂，但这并非真相。为我取来这符文，以我们通常的方式纪念其灵魂。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good."
msgstr "很好。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just do it later on."
msgstr "以后再做吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"A vampire's death is a big success to those elderly jerks. Well, it is their"
" belief that can't be bothered in any way."
msgstr "吸血鬼的死亡对那些老混蛋来说是一大胜利。好吧，这是他们的信仰，无论如何都无需在意。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Got it?"
msgstr "明白了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I thank you for this rune.\n"
"*Shatters it by hand*\n"
msgstr ""
"我感谢你带来这符文。\n"
"*用手捏碎它*\n"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just thanks..."
msgstr "只是感谢……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*smirks*"
msgstr "*得意地笑*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Take Vampire to the Cove"
msgstr "带吸血鬼去海湾"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Take Vampire to the Cove'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Escort the vampire to the <color_light_blue>vampire cove</color>."
msgstr "护送吸血鬼到<color_light_blue>吸血鬼海湾</color>。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "This is the last job, you want to do it?"
msgstr "这是最后一项任务，你想做吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Since you've been helping me for a while, I will need you to travel with me "
"to the vampire cove. Being isolated for centuries is a great experience, but"
" seeing a living community of my kind alleviates my frozen body the most."
msgstr "既然你帮了我一段时间，我需要你陪我前往吸血鬼海湾。被孤立数百年是种难得的体验，但看到同类的活生生的群落最能温暖我冰冷的身躯。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Good, those tests proved yourself a good descendant. As a reward, I'll "
"protect you along the way."
msgstr "很好，那些考验证明你是个优秀的后裔。作为奖励，我会在路上保护你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just okay, get back later..."
msgstr "还行吧，以后再来……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"This may be a long journey. You know I'm a night creature, so you'll have to"
" take care of me in daytime."
msgstr "这可能是一段漫长的旅程。你知道我是夜行生物，所以白天你得照顾我。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What?"
msgstr "什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I see my kindred seems alright. Well, it does matter to me, and you've been "
"the key to this. Thank you, descendant."
msgstr "看来我的族人似乎没事。嗯，这对我很重要，而你是关键。谢谢你，后裔。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Get 2 Corrupt Bloodrune Stone"
msgstr "获取2块腐化血符石"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Get 2 Corrupt Bloodrune Stone'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Get the <color_light_red>2 corrupted bloodrune stones</color> that are "
"dropped by killing the <color_magenta>infected vampires</color> then deliver"
" them to the trader."
msgstr ""
"获取<color_light_red>2块腐化血符石</color>，通过击杀<color_magenta>受感染的吸血鬼</color>掉落，然后交给商人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, actually we have a problem..."
msgstr "嗯，实际上我们有个问题……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Our kin isn't a target of diseases, but those 2 vampires at the back, they "
"really look bad and start raging on its own, so we cage them at early "
"state... Never knew the magic was that strong enough to kill EVEN us. I want"
" you to end the sick vampires as your task and get their corrupted "
"bloodrune. We know we can dispose them easily, but our beliefs prevent us "
"from killing our own kind."
msgstr ""
"我们的族人本不该成为疾病的目标，但后面那两只吸血鬼，它们状况很糟，开始自行狂暴，所以我们早期就把它们关起来了……从不知道魔法竟强大到连我们都能杀死。我希望你作为任务去终结那些病态吸血鬼，并获取它们的腐化血符石。我们知道可以轻易处理它们，但我们的信仰禁止我们杀害同类。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Thank you, now go."
msgstr "谢谢，现在去吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "You need to do that later."
msgstr "你需要稍后再做。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Serious pain you'll get from breaking into their cage."
msgstr "闯入它们的笼子会让你遭受剧痛。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What happened there?"
msgstr "那里发生了什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Great, mortal. This oozing bloodrune will now meet its place... Or not at "
"all."
msgstr "很好，凡人。这渗血的符石现在将找到它的归宿……或者根本不会。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "*glaressharply*"
msgstr "*锐利地瞪视*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Slay 10 bats"
msgstr "击杀10只蝙蝠"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Slay 10 bats'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Kill <color_magenta>10 bats</color> then talk to the trader after "
"completion. <color_magenta>Bats</color> are commonly seen at "
"<color_gray>nighttime</color> or inside a <color_light_blue>cave</color>."
msgstr ""
"杀死<color_magenta>10只蝙蝠</color>，完成后与商人交谈。<color_magenta>蝙蝠</color>常见于<color_gray>夜间</color>或<color_light_blue>洞穴</color>内。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "We do appreciate your assistance with our needs."
msgstr "我们确实感谢你协助满足我们的需求。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Vampire bats became literal bloodsuckers these passing days and I want you "
"to hunt down 10 of these vermins. We've been swarmed by these creatures "
"lately but gladly we managed to shove them away."
msgstr "这些天来，吸血蝙蝠真的成了吸血的害虫，我要你猎杀10只这些害兽。我们最近被这些生物包围，但幸好我们设法赶走了它们。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good. Come back anytime you want."
msgstr "很好。随时可以回来。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I guess you're afraid of bats..."
msgstr "我猜你害怕蝙蝠……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bats are nocturnal, and tends to live in dark places like caves."
msgstr "蝙蝠是夜行性的，倾向于生活在黑暗的地方，比如洞穴。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Thank you for your help in eradicating some bloodsuckers."
msgstr "感谢你帮忙清除了一些吸血者。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Go to a forgotten burial site"
msgstr "前往一处被遗忘的墓地"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to a forgotten burial site'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
" Travel to a <color_light_blue>burial site</color> then talk to the seeker."
msgstr "前往<color_light_blue>墓地</color>，然后与寻访者交谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Before we go, the trader asked me a request on this journey."
msgstr "出发前，商人向我提出了这次旅程的一个请求。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"The trader told me to observe the old graveyards we knew from the past. So "
"before we go to the outskirts, we'll get pass through it first."
msgstr "商人让我观察我们过去所知的古老墓地。所以在前往郊区之前，我们会先经过那里。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Off we go, mortal."
msgstr "出发吧，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, that's your choice..."
msgstr "好吧，这是你的选择……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Its been a long time since I see those graves..."
msgstr "我已经很久没见过那些坟墓了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "What now?"
msgstr "现在怎么办？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"The magic took over the buried corpses? That's unfortunate and the trader "
"would be disappointed about this..."
msgstr "魔法控制了埋葬的尸体？这真不幸，商人会对此感到失望的……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Go to the wasteland outskirts"
msgstr "前往废土郊区"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Go to the wasteland outskirts'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Along with the seeker, travel to the <color_light_blue>wasteland "
"outskirts</color>. Talk to them again after reaching the destination."
msgstr "与寻访者一同前往<color_light_blue>废土郊区</color>。到达目的地后再次与他们交谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Are we ready for this trip?"
msgstr "我们准备好这次旅行了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"We are now going to the outskirts, and I know the commando told you about "
"this place."
msgstr "我们现在要去郊区了，我知道突击队员告诉过你这个地方。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Good. Now off we go, mortal."
msgstr "很好。现在出发吧，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "..."
msgstr "..."

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I'll give you some details about the outskirts. It is a large structure with"
" barricaded walls and tents placed outside for human survivors. It also has "
"a barn and farm fields that provides descent food, and shopkeepers sell "
"various stuff there."
msgstr "我会告诉你一些关于郊区的细节。它是一个大型建筑，有围墙和帐篷供人类幸存者居住。那里还有一个谷仓和农田，提供充足的食物，店主们出售各种物品。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"\"What else could I do for you\" you say? Don't worry, I have no more "
"requests for you. Ask anyone here if you're curious. When you're done, talk "
"to me."
msgstr "你说“我还能为你做什么”？别担心，我没有更多请求了。如果你好奇，可以问问这里的任何人。完成后，再跟我谈谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Ummm...."
msgstr "嗯……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Recruit Radio Specialist"
msgstr "招募无线电专家"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Recruit Radio Specialist'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Ask the <color_yellow>Radio Specialist</color> to join, then talk to the "
"guard after they did."
msgstr "邀请<color_yellow>无线电专家</color>加入，然后在他们同意后与守卫交谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "It's easy, I think..."
msgstr "我想这很简单……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"First things first, we have to build a radio tower that transmit signals to "
"our fellow survivors out in the wilds which serves as their waypoint to our "
"place. Well, building that cheap structure is simple, but what I want you to"
" do is to find a person with expertise to operate this kind of stuff."
msgstr ""
"首先，我们必须建造一座无线电塔，向荒野中的幸存者发送信号，作为他们找到我们这里的路标。嗯，建造那个廉价结构很简单，但我想让你做的是找一个有专业知识的人来操作这类设备。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Great. Now move, mortal."
msgstr "很好。现在行动吧，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Great! Let this survivors die out of nowhere then..."
msgstr "太好了！那就让这些幸存者莫名其妙地死去吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just bring them in safely."
msgstr "只要安全地把他们带进来就行。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Where are they?"
msgstr "他们在哪里？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "I knew you can bring one. Now let this nerd go to work!"
msgstr "我就知道你能带一个回来。现在让这个书呆子去工作吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Slay the succumbed vampire"
msgstr "击杀堕落的吸血鬼"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Slay the succumbed vampire'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Kill the <color_magenta>succumbed vampire</color> then talk to the guard.\n"
"<color_red>Going unprepared is a death trap!</color>"
msgstr ""
"杀死<color_magenta>堕落的吸血鬼</color>，然后与守卫交谈。\n"
"<color_red>毫无准备就去是自寻死路！</color>"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With the radio working well, we will be able to connect to the outsiders and"
" hope for them to receive our message. Yet there's this vampire I am worried"
" about, wandering the cursed lands and wicked to its vile nature. Our "
"scouting patrol knows the coordinates, and I want you to put it down "
"immediately before it brings wrath to other survivors."
msgstr ""
"无线电运行良好后，我们将能够联系外界，希望他们能收到我们的信息。但我担心那个吸血鬼，它在诅咒之地游荡，本性邪恶。我们的侦察巡逻队知道坐标，我希望你立即解决它，以免它给其他幸存者带来灾祸。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With it wielding the power of an immortal, provoking unprepared is a "
"suicidal act."
msgstr "它拥有不朽的力量，贸然挑衅是自杀行为。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "The monster does not rest after a kill..."
msgstr "那怪物杀人后不会停歇……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Bring guns and keep your distance, us vampires will take down humans for "
"almost instantly."
msgstr "带上枪并保持距离，我们吸血鬼几乎能瞬间击倒人类。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Is it dead?"
msgstr "它死了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Fascinating job mortal! With its death, others will be safe... A bit."
msgstr "干得漂亮，凡人！它一死，其他人就安全了……暂时安全。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Destroy the vampirus"
msgstr "摧毁吸血鬼巢穴"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Destroy the vampirus'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With the help of the <color_yellow>seeker</color>, locate and destroy the <color_light_blue>vampirus</color>, the place where <color_magenta>infected vampires</color> gather.\n"
"<color_red>Going unprepared is a death trap!</color>"
msgstr ""
"在<color_yellow>寻路者</color>的帮助下，定位并摧毁<color_light_blue>吸血鬼巢穴</color>，那是<color_magenta>受感染的吸血鬼</color>聚集的地方。\n"
"<color_red>毫无准备就去是自寻死路！</color>"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, that vampire is not alone.\n"
"\n"
"I have recently received a radio message that reveals the pinpoint location of the gathering place owned by those infected vampires. Your task is to find a way to stop and annihilate the entire army of them. I told the seeker about it and she'll help you infiltrate your objective."
msgstr ""
"不幸的是，那个吸血鬼并非孤身一人。\n"
"\n"
"我最近收到一条无线电信息，揭示了那些受感染吸血鬼拥有的聚集地的精确位置。你的任务是设法阻止并歼灭它们的整个军团。我已告知寻路者此事，她会帮你潜入目标地点。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Good. Just remind her about it and she'll provide the essential information."
msgstr "很好。只要提醒她一下，她就会提供必要的信息。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Alright then, let's talk about it again later..."
msgstr "好吧，那我们晚点再谈这个……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Be aware. If alone is dangerous, more so when they're dozen."
msgstr "小心点。单独一个就很危险，成群结队时更甚。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Report?"
msgstr "报告？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Unbelievable! You did it, mortal! Our master would be grateful of your "
"doings!"
msgstr "难以置信！你做到了，凡人！我们的主人会感激你的所作所为！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Travel to the vampirus"
msgstr "前往吸血鬼巢穴"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Travel to the vampirus'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Along with the seeker, travel to the <color_light_blue>vampirus</color>."
msgstr "与探索者一同前往<color_light_blue>吸血鬼巢穴</color>。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Lead the trail, I'm right behind if you require my assistance."
msgstr "带路吧，如果需要我的帮助，我就在你身后。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Keep an eye out for possible threats along the way."
msgstr "沿途留意可能的威胁。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Are we in our destination?"
msgstr "我们到目的地了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Now that we're here, we have to locate the entrance that leads to the "
"depths."
msgstr "既然到了这里，我们必须找到通往深处的入口。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Unseal the entrance"
msgstr "解除入口封印"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Unseal the entrance'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Protect the seeker from the <color_magenta>zeds</color> attracted to your "
"location."
msgstr "保护探索者免受被吸引到你们位置的<color_magenta>僵尸</color>伤害。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Yes, I can unseal it at this point."
msgstr "是的，我现在可以解除它。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"I do not guarantee our safety from breaking the seal, so you'll need to "
"guard me as I break it."
msgstr "我不能保证打破封印时我们的安全，所以你需要在我打破它时保护我。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"With the smell of blood coming out of the vampirus, zombies are attracted "
"towards our location."
msgstr "随着吸血鬼巢穴散发出的血腥味，僵尸被吸引到我们的位置。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "And now that the seal is broken, we can go through it."
msgstr "现在封印已破，我们可以通过了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bring Radio Specialist to the outskirts"
msgstr "将无线电专家带到外围"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Bring Radio Specialist to the
#. outskirts'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Escort the specialist to the <color_light_blue>wasteland outskirts</color>."
msgstr "护送专家到<color_light_blue>废土外围</color>。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "We're going, right?"
msgstr "我们要出发了，对吧？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "We have to go to that place and I need you to lead the way."
msgstr "我们必须去那个地方，我需要你带路。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Just remember to keep everything fine as we go there."
msgstr "只要记住，在我们去那里的路上保持一切顺利。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, your words are useless..."
msgstr "好吧，你的话毫无用处……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "From what direction did you came from? I suppose that's the right way."
msgstr "你是从哪个方向来的？我想那条路是对的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"This place looks neat! Now that I'm here, I'll do my job as you have said "
"earlier."
msgstr "这地方看起来真整洁！既然我来了，我会按你之前说的做我的工作。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Bring Prisoner to the outskirts"
msgstr "将囚犯带到郊外"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Bring Prisoner to the outskirts'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Take the prisoner to the <color_light_blue>wasteland outskirts</color>."
msgstr "将囚犯带到<color_light_blue>废土郊外</color>。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Lead me to that place, then..."
msgstr "带我去那个地方，然后……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Awesome!"
msgstr "太棒了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Well, atleast you've made me happy before my fate..."
msgstr "好吧，至少你在我的命运降临前让我开心了一下……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"You need my advice for this? I could say something if I'm already free in "
"the wilderness..."
msgstr "这事你需要我的建议？要是我已经在荒野自由了，我倒是能说点什么……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Damn! This place is like a fortress! But you should've warned me about the "
"vampires living here... They freak me out everytime I see one..."
msgstr "该死！这地方像个堡垒！但你该早点警告我这里有吸血鬼的……每次看到他们我都吓得够呛……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Reach a memorial crypt"
msgstr "抵达一座纪念墓穴"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Reach a memorial crypt'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Travel to a <color_light_blue>memorial crypt</color> then inspect its "
"surroundings."
msgstr "前往<color_light_blue>纪念墓穴</color>并探查其周围环境。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid "Dark Descendant"
msgstr "黑暗后裔"

#. ~ Description for mission '{'str': 'Dark Descendant'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission.json
msgid ""
"Ask a <color_yellow>lone vampire</color> to join your party.\n"
"You must earn their trust by doing their favor."
msgstr ""
"邀请一位<color_yellow>独行吸血鬼</color>加入你的队伍。\n"
"你必须通过帮助他们来赢得信任。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "corrupted bloodrune stone"
msgid_plural "corrupted bloodrune stones"
msgstr[0] "腐化的血符石"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'corrupted bloodrune stone'}
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"A black, gooey bloodrune stone specifically owned by an infected vampire. It"
" no longer pulsate and the markings are completely erased."
msgstr "一块黑色、黏稠的血符石，专属于受感染的吸血鬼。它已不再搏动，表面的符文也完全消失了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "small leech tooth"
msgid_plural "small leech teeth"
msgstr[0] "小型水蛭齿"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'small leech tooth', 'str_pl': 'small leech
#. teeth'}
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid ""
"A tooth size of the human fingernails. It is sharp, but too small to be used"
" as a tool."
msgstr "一颗如人类指甲盖大小的牙齿。它很锋利，但太小了，无法用作工具。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "blood sac"
msgid_plural "blood sacs"
msgstr[0] "血囊"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'blood sac'}
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_mission_items.json
msgid "The large sac of the devourer leech."
msgstr "吞噬水蛭的巨大囊袋。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"It was my time to hunt down a prey. Moon's in its peak, everything's "
"peaceful... But all crumbles so quickly that night, after sighting this "
"woman at the forest trail, weeping, tending to her grievous wound."
msgstr "那是我外出狩猎的时刻。月正当空，万物宁静……但那一夜，在森林小径上瞥见这个女人后，一切迅速崩塌——她正哭泣着，照料自己严重的伤口。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "What about her?."
msgstr "她怎么了？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "Her wound?"
msgstr "她的伤口呢？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "<done_conversation_section>"
msgstr "<done_conversation_section>"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "<end_talking>"
msgstr "<end_talking>"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"From my observation, she's at her mid-life, fully dressed with her bag full "
"of supplies."
msgstr "据我观察，她正值中年，衣着整齐，背包里装满了补给品。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "What about her wound?"
msgstr "她的伤口是怎么回事？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"I did not come closer, but I took a deeper look. From what I have seen, "
"there's this gooey black substance, pumping slowly into her."
msgstr "我没有靠近，但仔细看了看。我看到有一种黏糊糊的黑色物质，正缓缓注入她体内。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "Do you have any idea what it is?"
msgstr "你知道那是什么吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "No. But in my belief, its a parasite that sucks life from its host."
msgstr "不知道。但我相信，那是一种从宿主身上吸取生命的寄生虫。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "So, what did you do after that?"
msgstr "那么，之后你做了什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"I stalked her through the trail. My curiosity kept my thirst aside for some "
"moment, 'till she suddenly spasms to the ground. I approach her and inspect "
"his vitality, finding out she's dead. Her veins turn black and her eyes "
"oozing with goo. I tried to close her eyelids, but then she immediately bit "
"my <swear> hand!"
msgstr ""
"我沿着小径跟踪她。好奇心暂时压住了我的饥渴，直到她突然痉挛倒地。我靠近她，检查她的生命迹象，发现她已经死了。她的血管变黑，眼睛渗出黏液。我试图合上她的眼皮，但她立刻咬了我的<swear>手！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid "Woah, that is horrifying!"
msgstr "哇，太可怕了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\lonevamp_s1.json
msgid ""
"In quick response, I slam her <swear> head against the ground and explodes into a mass of gore!\n"
"Well, fortunately her bite isn't that deep, but I swear I'll <swear> break their skulls before I get too close to them again!"
msgstr ""
"我迅速反应，把她的<swear>头砸向地面，炸成一团血肉！\n"
"好吧，幸好她咬得不算深，但我发誓，下次再靠近它们之前，我一定会<swear>打碎它们的头骨！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\Backgrounds\v_background_list.json
msgid "<BGSS_intro_question>"
msgstr "<BGSS_intro_question>"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Here's your blood."
msgstr "这是你的血。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Here's your bloodrune stone."
msgstr "这是你的血符文石。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Greetings, human."
msgstr "你好，人类。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "What is it, mortal?"
msgstr "什么事，凡人？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Speak up, mortal."
msgstr "说吧，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Tell me about yourself."
msgstr "说说你自己。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Why are you here?"
msgstr "你为什么在这里？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Greetings, my brethren."
msgstr "你好，我的同胞。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "About that quest..."
msgstr "关于那个任务……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Ummm... You want to stick with me?"
msgstr "呃……你想跟着我吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I'm vacant for your needs."
msgstr "我随时待命，满足你的需求。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Sorry to bother."
msgstr "抱歉打扰了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am a vampire, preserved for centuries. But you see, I enshroud myself in "
"the shadows of the past."
msgstr "我是一名吸血鬼，已存世数百年。但你看，我将自己隐藏在往昔的阴影之中。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Preserved?"
msgstr "存世？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay."
msgstr "好的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"I live here as my peaceful sanctuary for a very long time. Though the world "
"is in chaos, I am not bothered nor assaulted by those things."
msgstr "长久以来，我将此地作为宁静的庇护所。尽管世界陷入混乱，我却不受那些事物的侵扰或袭击。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Is there a some sort of place like this?"
msgstr "有这样的地方存在吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Okay then..."
msgstr "好吧，那么……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"That marking... I see you've been helping my kindred with their troubles."
msgstr "那个标记……看来你一直在帮助我的同族解决麻烦。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Just like others, you want me as a slave... I refuse, mortal."
msgstr "和其他人一样，你想让我当奴隶……我拒绝，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I just want you as an odd friend... I'm sorry."
msgstr "我只是想和你做个特别的朋友……对不起。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I want you to go on a journey with me."
msgstr "我希望你能陪我踏上旅程。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "No, I want you to go on a journey with me."
msgstr "不，是我要你陪我踏上旅程。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"It is the prowess that all immortals have, and we tend to refine this by "
"concealing ourselves from humanity."
msgstr "这是所有不朽者都具备的能力，我们倾向于通过隐匿于人类视线之外来精进此道。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Too bad."
msgstr "真可惜。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"Yes it is. Its a small community of night creatures tending to theirselves "
"to live in peace."
msgstr "是的。那是一个夜行生物的小型社群，他们致力于和平共处。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "So, where do I find this place?"
msgstr "那么，我该去哪里找到这个地方？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"Do not bring me to my death. I will leave MY territory and expect benefits "
"believing in you."
msgstr "别带我去送死。我会离开我的领地，并期待因信任你而获得好处。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I promise..."
msgstr "我保证……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I already said I refuse... NOW, I have to kill you for your ignorance!"
msgstr "我已经说过我拒绝……现在，我必须因你的无知而杀了你！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "KILL ME IF YOU CAN!!!"
msgstr "有本事就来杀我啊！！！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "These places could be anywhere far from human civilizations."
msgstr "这些地方可能远离人类文明的任何角落。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Nope. Even if I know, I won't tell you."
msgstr "不。就算我知道，也不会告诉你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Thanks, I guess..."
msgstr "谢了，大概吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "You sure about that?"
msgstr "你确定吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Yes, I do."
msgstr "是的，我确定。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "I take back what I've said..."
msgstr "我收回之前说过的话……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"No, I have no more requests for you. You have helped me alot and proven me "
"your worth. As a reward, I'll give you my mark of trust on you."
msgstr "不，我没有更多请求了。你帮了我很多，也证明了自己的价值。作为奖励，我将赐予你我的信任印记。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Thank you for this mark... Let's go!"
msgstr "感谢这份印记……我们出发吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid ""
"You think I'm foolish to believe you as my kind? Trust me, mortal, us "
"vampires are not born by drinking artificial drugs."
msgstr "你以为我会蠢到相信你是我同类？相信我，凡人，我们吸血鬼可不是靠喝人造药物诞生的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Isolated\v_lo_responses.json
msgid "Well, atleast I'm alot stronger than you."
msgstr "好吧，至少我比你强得多。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Here's your small leech teeth."
msgstr "这是你的小型水蛭齿。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Here's your blood sac."
msgstr "这是你的血囊。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "You got something to say, descendant?."
msgstr "后裔，你有话要说吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Mortal descendant... What do I expect from you?"
msgstr "凡人的后裔……我能指望你什么呢？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk with you."
msgstr "我想和你谈谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Any work can I do?."
msgstr "有什么我能做的工作吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I've done the final test... So, what now?"
msgstr "我已经完成了最终测试……那么，现在呢？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "About your command..."
msgstr "关于你的命令……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I should go now."
msgstr "我该走了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "So descendant... What should we talk about?"
msgstr "那么后裔……我们该聊些什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Topic?"
msgstr "话题？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Who are you?"
msgstr "你是谁？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Wait... Vampire with a gun?"
msgstr "等等……吸血鬼用枪？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "News about the outside world, sir?"
msgstr "先生，有外界的消息吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Do you offer your guns in trading?"
msgstr "你交易枪支吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Let's talk later."
msgstr "我们晚点再聊。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I guess I've asked everything..."
msgstr "我想我已经问完所有问题了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I am a vampire, guarding this place from any kinds of threat."
msgstr "我是吸血鬼，负责守卫此地，抵御任何威胁。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "So, are you the owner of this refugee?"
msgstr "那么，你是这个避难所的主人吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Sorry about it..."
msgstr "对此我很抱歉……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "You thought we can't use this things? You are wrong, descendant!"
msgstr "你以为我们用不了这些东西？你错了，后裔！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Umm... Okay."
msgstr "呃……好吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I have no idea. Its been decades since I traveled into this cove."
msgstr "我不知道。我来到这个海湾已经几十年了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Oh. Okay."
msgstr "哦。好吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Nope. To trade a gun like this, you better find a gunshop."
msgstr "不。要交易这样的枪，你最好去找枪店。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "A gunshop?"
msgstr "枪店？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "No. This is owned and built by HIM."
msgstr "不。这是由祂拥有并建造的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Who is HIM?"
msgstr "祂是谁？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid ""
"She's at the wasteland outskirts, a place where vampires freely communicate "
"with you all. Sounds wonderful, right?"
msgstr "她在废土外围，一个吸血鬼能自由与你们交流的地方。听起来很棒，对吧？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Wonderful? I don't even know where it is!"
msgstr "很棒？我连它在哪都不知道！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid ""
"HIM is our master, our lord, the almighty one. HE brought us into existence,"
" and we owe our life serving HIS will."
msgstr "祂是我们的主人，我们的主宰，全能的存在。祂赋予我们生命，我们以侍奉祂的意志为生。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "I'd wish to meet HIM..."
msgstr "我真希望能见到祂……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid ""
"\"What now\" you say? The tests I have given you has to proven yourself "
"worthy to push forward the boundary between this cave and the outskirt. Now,"
" take this ring and tell the seeker about the outskirts, she'll talk about "
"and guide you to its coordinates. The gunshop has something to give when you"
" arrive, so make sure you wear the ring before speaking to her."
msgstr ""
"“现在怎么办”你说？我给你的测试已经证明你值得推进这个洞穴与郊区的边界。现在，拿着这枚戒指，告诉寻者关于郊区的事，她会谈论并指引你到它的坐标。当你到达时，枪店有东西要给你，所以确保在和她说话前戴上戒指。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_uc_responses.json
msgid "Yes. I'll do as you say and thank you for this ring."
msgstr "是的。我会照你说的做，并感谢你给的这枚戒指。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "You look important."
msgstr "你看起来很重要。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Mortal... You're up to nothing?"
msgstr "凡人……你没什么事吧？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Where am I?"
msgstr "我在哪里？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "I'd be going now..."
msgstr "我现在要走了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Just an assigned guard here, nothing happened 'till you came in."
msgstr "只是个被指派在这里的守卫，直到你进来前都没发生什么。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Why should I? If you want answers, go ask my partner."
msgstr "我为什么要？如果你想要答案，去问我的搭档。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I like you."
msgstr "我喜欢你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "You think I'm a dummy? Stop repeating your question, kid!"
msgstr "你以为我是傻瓜吗？别再重复你的问题了，小子！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Sorry..."
msgstr "抱歉……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I know you know where you are. *grins*."
msgstr "我知道你清楚自己在哪。*咧嘴笑*。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Geez, don't show that to me."
msgstr "天哪，别把那东西给我看。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Okay, okay."
msgstr "好吧，好吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Now I know where we are."
msgstr "现在我知道我们在哪了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Shut up mortal, everyone does like me."
msgstr "闭嘴凡人，每个人都喜欢我。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Oh..."
msgstr "哦……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "If you're here to fuck us up, I'd really need to slay you immediately!"
msgstr "如果你是来捣乱的，我真的需要立刻宰了你！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I apologize for my mistake."
msgstr "我为我的错误道歉。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "YEAH GIRL! BRING IT!"
msgstr "没错姑娘！放马过来！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Damn, you managed to wear that."
msgstr "该死，你居然能穿上那个。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Mortal, You look dazzled?"
msgstr "凡人，你看上去眼花缭乱？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Tell me who you are."
msgstr "告诉我你是谁。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I'm vacant for jobs."
msgstr "我空闲着，可以接活。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Bye..."
msgstr "再见……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I don't actually have a problem, but others could have."
msgstr "我其实没问题，但别人可能会有。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I'll ask them."
msgstr "我会问问他们。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I'm a guardian, defending our cave from unwelcome intruders like you."
msgstr "我是守卫，保护我们的洞穴免受像你这样的不速之客侵扰。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Whoa, I'm not here to pick fights."
msgstr "哇，我不是来打架的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Nice..."
msgstr "不错……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"You're on the vampire cove, a refugee itself. This is our place with peace "
"and sure living for centuries for us all. After that magical outbreak, we "
"are forced to eat and drink certain foodstuff like animal meat chunks and "
"its blood, but we never tried to consume rotten flesh from those frenzied "
"humans."
msgstr ""
"你在吸血鬼海湾，这里本身是个避难所。几个世纪以来，这是我们所有人和平安稳生活的地方。那次魔法爆发后，我们被迫食用特定食物，比如动物肉块和血液，但我们从未尝试吃那些疯狂人类的腐肉。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "It's not magical, it's Cataclysm."
msgstr "那不是魔法，是大灾变。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Oh great."
msgstr "哦，太好了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"You should be. We never, EVER let any humans come into our beloved home. "
"Until we are commanded to accompany with your kind."
msgstr "你该庆幸。我们从未，绝对从未让任何人类进入我们珍爱的家园。直到我们被命令与你们这类人相伴。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Who commanded you?"
msgstr "谁命令你的？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Oh... Seems you are forced to talk with me."
msgstr "哦……看来你被迫和我说话。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"Cataclysm? So you humans made those thingies... Well, I can't blame you for "
"that."
msgstr "大灾变？所以是你们人类搞出那些玩意儿……好吧，我不能为此责怪你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "You're right..."
msgstr "你说得对……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"You look concerned, but I'll never let a word come out from my mouth about "
"HIM."
msgstr "你看起来很在意，但我绝不会从我嘴里说出关于他的一个字。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Never knew you're loyal..."
msgstr "从不知道你这么忠诚……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "What do you need?."
msgstr "你需要什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Nothing..."
msgstr "没什么……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "What are you doing here?"
msgstr "你在这里做什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I was tasked to watch over the two rampaging kindreds in their cages."
msgstr "我被指派看守笼子里那两个狂暴的同族。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Oh, okay..."
msgstr "哦，好吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "May I kill those two vampires?."
msgstr "我可以杀掉那两个吸血鬼吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid ""
"Ofcourse, you can! We already have lost our faith on them to fight back "
"their rabid sickness."
msgstr "当然可以！我们已经对他们能抵抗狂犬病失去信心了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "That's too bad..."
msgstr "那太糟糕了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "Just staying in the darkness... Away from the horrifying magic."
msgstr "只是待在黑暗中……远离那可怕的魔法。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ug_responses.json
msgid "I guess you're afraid of Cataclysm..."
msgstr "我猜你害怕大灾变……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Can you tell me who you are?"
msgstr "你能告诉我你是谁吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "About our journey..."
msgstr "关于我们的旅程……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Jobs to work?"
msgstr "有工作要做吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "They've let me help in their troubles."
msgstr "他们让我帮忙解决他们的麻烦。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "We need to go to the vampirus."
msgstr "我们需要去吸血鬼那里。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "About our job..."
msgstr "关于我们的工作……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "...?"
msgstr "……？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"I see you've been working hard to help us on our problems... Nice meeting "
"you and I apologize for ignoring you from the start I glanced on your eyes."
msgstr "我看到你一直在努力帮助我们解决问题……很高兴认识你，我为一开始忽视你而道歉，当时我瞥见了你的眼睛。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "As I was saying..."
msgstr "正如我刚才所说……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am the seeker of this cave, and my job is to scout the surrounding areas "
"for possible threats."
msgstr "我是这个洞穴的探索者，我的工作是侦察周围区域，寻找可能的威胁。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "What kind of threats?"
msgstr "什么样的威胁？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay..."
msgstr "好吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Nothing dangerous, its all the same everytime."
msgstr "没什么危险的，每次都是一样。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Well, okay."
msgstr "好吧，行。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"Good. If you need me to come along, just tell me and I will help you in your"
" troubles."
msgstr "很好。如果你需要我跟着，尽管告诉我，我会帮你解决麻烦。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Come with me."
msgstr "跟我来。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Job's too easy to bring you along."
msgstr "这活儿太简单了，用不着你跟着。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Lead the way, descendant."
msgstr "带路吧，后裔。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Let's go!"
msgstr "我们走吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "As you say, descendant..."
msgstr "如你所言，后裔……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Bye."
msgstr "再见。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Descendant, are you sure about this?"
msgstr "后裔，你确定要这么做吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Yes."
msgstr "是的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Tell me the problem, descendant."
msgstr "告诉我问题所在，后裔。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "We can't go down the slope."
msgstr "我们下不去这个斜坡。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Nevermind..."
msgstr "算了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "Doing this job takes time..."
msgstr "做这活儿需要时间……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid ""
"Hmm, these bastards has sealed the entrance. I didn't expect for them to use"
" a spell, even tho they're heavily influenced by the magic..."
msgstr "嗯，这些混蛋把入口封住了。我没想到他们会用法术，尽管他们深受魔法影响……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "So, can you unseal the entrance?"
msgstr "那么，你能解开入口的封印吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_us_responses.json
msgid "I must perform this at night by the entrance."
msgstr "我必须在夜晚于入口处进行这个仪式。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Here's your corrupted bloodrune stones."
msgstr "这是你的腐化血符石。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Do you need something, mortal?."
msgstr "你需要什么吗，凡人？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Want something?"
msgstr "想要点什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Tell me what happened outside."
msgstr "告诉我外面发生了什么。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "I'll trade with ya..."
msgstr "我来跟你交易……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "You need help? I'm here to do it."
msgstr "你需要帮助吗？我来帮你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "About your quest..."
msgstr "关于你的任务……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Bye, see you later."
msgstr "再见，回头见。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am assigned as a trader by my master. I sell our artifact materials used "
"in forging vampiric stuff. Or buy an already forged ones for a higher trade "
"value."
msgstr "我被主人指派为商人。我出售用于锻造吸血鬼物品的我们的神器材料。或者以更高的交易价值购买已锻造好的成品。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Wait. Why are you selling artifacts?"
msgstr "等等。你为什么要出售神器？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Why the hell are you accepting human stuff in trading?"
msgstr "你他妈的为什么在交易中接受人类的东西？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Okay!."
msgstr "好的！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"I have no idea what's happening outside right now. I came here without "
"sunburn after taking orders from HIM."
msgstr "我现在不知道外面发生了什么。我听从了“他”的命令来到这里，没有晒伤。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Well, I expected nothing..."
msgstr "好吧，我本来也没指望什么……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"Our master wants to help the last, surviving humans in our utmost "
"solution... Share our power with you all. But he still wants an official "
"trading, so you need lots of valuables or cash buying our items."
msgstr ""
"我们的主人想帮助最后幸存的人类，用我们最极致的解决方案……与你们所有人分享我们的力量。但他仍然想要正式的交易，所以你需要大量的贵重物品或现金来购买我们的物品。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Oh... Just great."
msgstr "哦……真是太好了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"I don't know. Our master said we have to accept any valuables you humans got"
" in your trip."
msgstr "我不知道。我们的主人说我们必须接受你们人类在旅途中获得的任何贵重物品。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Master? Could you tell me anything about this HIM?"
msgstr "主人？你能告诉我关于这个“他”的任何事吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Nope. HE remains a mystery to all of you."
msgstr "不行。“他”对你们所有人来说仍然是个谜。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Damn... You can't tell even HIS face."
msgstr "该死……你甚至连“他”的脸都不能说。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid ""
"HIM is our master, the reason of our immortality and existence in this "
"damned world."
msgstr "“他”是我们的主人，是我们在这个该死的世界中不朽和存在的原因。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "So, where is HE?"
msgstr "那么，“他”在哪里？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "Don't even try to know..."
msgstr "别试图知道……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Underrefugee\v_ut_responses.json
msgid "No. I guess those problems are enough to help us out..."
msgstr "不。我想那些问题已经足够帮助我们了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Are you done?"
msgstr "你完成了吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Please help me... They... they're so... cruel..."
msgstr "请帮帮我……他们……他们太……残忍了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid ""
"Damn... those suckers... please I beg you to...\n"
"*cough*"
msgstr ""
"该死……那些混蛋……求你了，我恳求你……\n"
"*咳嗽*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid ""
"COME CLOSER OR I-I'LL... damn these <swear> suckers really took a piece out "
"of my sanity."
msgstr "再靠近我就……我-我会……该死的这些<swear>混蛋真的快把我逼疯了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "TOUCH ME AND I'LL!... oh... you're not a monster..."
msgstr "敢碰我我就！……哦……你不是怪物……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "It's okay, I'm here to set you free."
msgstr "没事的，我是来解救你的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Sorry, I can't help you out. I have things to deal with."
msgstr "抱歉，我帮不了你。我还有事要处理。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "I don't take a weakling along with me. Now run."
msgstr "我不带累赘上路。现在快跑吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Bye? I guess..."
msgstr "再见？大概吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Not yet..."
msgstr "还不行……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Thank you so much!... But where do we go?"
msgstr "太感谢你了！……但我们该去哪儿？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "To the wasteland outskirts."
msgstr "去废土外围。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "I don't know, but stick with me and you'll be safe."
msgstr "我不知道，但跟着我你会安全的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Sounds cool!"
msgstr "听起来不错！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Yes it is..."
msgstr "是的……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "I owe my life to your kindness so... Lets go!"
msgstr "你的善意救了我的命……我们走吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "We go!"
msgstr "我们走！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid ""
"Wait! What if we help each other! I mean, I'll come assist you and set me "
"free after!"
msgstr "等等！如果我们互相帮助呢！我是说，我来协助你，然后你再放我自由！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "You're too weak to fight them."
msgstr "你太弱了，打不过他们。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Or just wait here and we'll get you out later."
msgstr "或者就待在这儿，我们稍后来救你。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Does that mean I can't leave this place?"
msgstr "这是不是意味着我离不开这里了？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Yea- I mean, never!"
msgstr "是的——我是说，绝对不会！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Yeah, but we'll be back to help you out."
msgstr "是的，但我们会回来帮你的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Thank you! I'll expect for you to come for me after this mess."
msgstr "谢谢！我期待你们在这混乱之后来找我。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "See you later."
msgstr "回头见。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Thank goodness! Please take me out of here."
msgstr "谢天谢地！请带我离开这里。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Not to be rude or anything but... Where will you take me to?"
msgstr "不是无礼或别的什么，但是……你要带我去哪里？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "After beating those monsters, I know you're too strong to protect me!"
msgstr "打败那些怪物后，我知道你太强了，保护不了我！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Vampirus\h_prison_cell.json
msgid "Well... Don't be timid to your belief."
msgstr "嗯……别对你的信仰胆怯。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Good to see ya, bud!"
msgstr "很高兴见到你，伙计！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Hello there traveler!"
msgstr "你好啊，旅行者！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Interested in my wares?!"
msgstr "对我的货物感兴趣吗？！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Who and what are you doing here?."
msgstr "你是谁，在这里做什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Any job to offer?."
msgstr "有什么工作可以提供吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "I want your junk..."
msgstr "我想要你的垃圾……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Just a silly guy collecting garbage outside, somewhere far from those "
"frenzied walkers. There are times my job put me into risks, so I only bring "
"few of them back here."
msgstr "只是个在外面收集垃圾的傻家伙，远离那些疯狂的步行者。有时我的工作会让我陷入风险，所以我只带少数回来这里。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "And... How's the living here?"
msgstr "那么……这里的生活怎么样？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Peaceful as always. But you see, life's been easier living along with these "
"vampires. They offer us protection from all sorts of threat while us humans "
"do the usual chores outside."
msgstr "一如既往地平静。但你看，和这些吸血鬼一起生活更容易。他们保护我们免受各种威胁，而我们人类在外面做日常杂务。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "I guess they're friendly afterall..."
msgstr "我想他们毕竟还是友好的……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"I have said my words clearly, or you like to repeat one's answer for fun?"
msgstr "我已经说得很清楚了，或者你喜欢重复别人的答案找乐子？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Sorry about that..."
msgstr "对此我很抱歉……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Hey buddy, I sell stuff here. Do you think I have a problem?\n"
"*Points a finger to his face*"
msgstr ""
"嘿伙计，我在这里卖东西。你觉得我有问题吗？\n"
"*用手指指着自己的脸*"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wjs_responses.json
msgid "Ummm... No."
msgstr "呃……没有。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Hey, what's up?"
msgstr "嘿，最近怎么样？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "What's happening here?."
msgstr "这里发生什么事了？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Want to come along?."
msgstr "想一起来吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "As usual. Repairs, gatherings, carnages... "
msgstr "和往常一样。修理、聚会、屠杀……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Are you sure about this? I could be a burden in your travels?"
msgstr "你确定要这样吗？我可能会成为你旅途中的累赘？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "I don't say I don't trust you, but no."
msgstr "我不是说不信任你，但不行。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Just follow me and we'll be fine."
msgstr "跟着我就好，我们会没事的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Just kiddin'."
msgstr "开个玩笑。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr1_responses.json
msgid "Bye then..."
msgstr "那就再见了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Hello outsider"
msgstr "你好，外来者"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk."
msgstr "我想谈谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Hi and bye."
msgstr "嗨，再见。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "About what?"
msgstr "关于什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Got a problem?"
msgstr "有问题吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid ""
"I guard here, most of the time. But sometimes I do few things other than "
"that."
msgstr "我大部分时间在这里守卫。但有时我也会做些别的事情。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Got it."
msgstr "明白了。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "Nope."
msgstr "不。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wr2_responses.json
msgid "You said it..."
msgstr "你说得对……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Bye now..."
msgstr "现在再见……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Don't waste your time talking to me at this point, just focus on the road!"
msgstr "别浪费时间跟我说话了，专心赶路吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Are you going to bring me there now?"
msgstr "你现在要带我去那里吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Well hi there? Its been a while since I see a living human walking in this "
"damned world!"
msgstr "哦，你好啊？我已经很久没看到活人在这该死的世界里行走了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "We need your help in operating a radio tower."
msgstr "我们需要你帮忙操作一个无线电塔。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Yes. I will."
msgstr "是的。我会的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Okay! I'll do it!"
msgstr "好的！我来做！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Radios are too simple to use, why'd would you want me to do it myself?"
msgstr "收音机用起来太简单了，你为什么要我自己动手？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "To ease the job?"
msgstr "为了减轻工作负担？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Increase the efficiency of our radio?"
msgstr "提高我们收音机的效率？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Its a complicated thing for us..."
msgstr "这对我们来说是个复杂的事情..."

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "We better get going."
msgstr "我们最好出发吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Forget it, I will come for as long as I gain benefits from doing this crap! "
"Besides, I am grateful that you've came to pick me up."
msgstr "算了，只要能从这破事里捞到好处，我就来！再说了，我很感激你来接我。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\h_wrs_responses.json
msgid "Lets go!"
msgstr "出发吧！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Mortal! Struggling to live?"
msgstr "凡人！挣扎求生吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Yes, and true."
msgstr "是的，而且没错。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Now, you want something from me?"
msgstr "现在，你想从我这儿得到什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Where did these guns came from?"
msgstr "这些枪是从哪儿来的？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "I want to buy."
msgstr "我想买。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Maybe later."
msgstr "也许晚点再说。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"I am the gun trader here... If you're not interested with my trades, just go"
" outside."
msgstr "我是这里的枪械商人...如果你对我的交易不感兴趣，就请出去吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Thanks for your info."
msgstr "谢谢你的信息。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"These are reserved from decades 'till now. Since there's no gunsmith on our "
"side, we only got few of them."
msgstr "这些是从几十年前保留到现在的。因为我们这边没有枪匠，所以只有少数几把。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Can I get something from you for free?"
msgstr "我能免费从你这儿拿点东西吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Sound hard-to-get."
msgstr "听起来很难搞到。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "I see that you've met my commander... What do you want?"
msgstr "我看到你见过我的指挥官了...你想要什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Ofcourse not! You want it, then buy it."
msgstr "当然不行！你想要，那就买吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Well, okay..."
msgstr "好吧，行吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "The commando told me about the supplies..."
msgstr "突击队员跟我提过补给的事……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"The supplies that were stocked in here are some spare draw kits, a bag and "
"blood powders. Will you take them?"
msgstr "这里存放的补给是一些备用抽血套件、一个袋子和血粉。你要拿走吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "But he told me to get some guns from you?"
msgstr "但他让我从你这儿拿些枪？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Okay, I'll take them!"
msgstr "好吧，我拿走了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"Umm... I could give you the oldest prototype of vampiric guns I got here:\n"
"The blood slinger."
msgstr ""
"呃……我可以给你我这儿最老的血族枪原型：\n"
"血弹发射器。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Seems legit. I'll take it!"
msgstr "看起来还行。我收下了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid ""
"I guess not... Its like a garbaged project you vampires been doing for these"
" days."
msgstr "我想还是算了……这就像是你们吸血鬼这些天搞的垃圾项目。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "I guess not..."
msgstr "我想还是算了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_vgs_responses.json
msgid "Tell him that we don't have any spare guns to give."
msgstr "告诉他我们没有多余的枪可以给。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You've come a long way, mortal."
msgstr "你走了很远的路啊，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "I know."
msgstr "我知道。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Yes, I know."
msgstr "是的，我知道。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk about something..."
msgstr "我想谈点事情……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Talk about what?"
msgstr "谈什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You should be safe here, so don't do anything stupid."
msgstr "你在这里应该是安全的，所以别做傻事。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Where am I?."
msgstr "我在哪儿？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "The commando has sent me to this place."
msgstr "突击队员派我来的这个地方。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You know a place like this?"
msgstr "你知道这样的地方吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "You need a volunteer for jobs?"
msgstr "你们需要志愿者干活吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay. Bye."
msgstr "好的。再见。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Nevermind. I'll be going now..."
msgstr "算了。我现在要走了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid ""
"You're in the sanctuary for both humans and vampires, the wasteland "
"outskirts. Here, we protect each other from savage entities and serves as an"
" outpost for those luckily survived ones."
msgstr "这里是人类与吸血鬼共同的庇护所，位于废土边缘。我们在此互相保护，抵御野蛮生物，并为那些侥幸幸存者提供前哨站。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Okay, thanks for the info."
msgstr "好的，谢谢告知。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid ""
"Hmm, so they have sent you here... For what reason? Everything's fine as it "
"is."
msgstr "嗯，所以他们派你来了……为了什么？现在一切都好好的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "So... Will you tell me where it is?"
msgstr "那么……你能告诉我它在哪儿吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "Oh, okay... Is there something I could help you with?"
msgstr "哦，好吧……有什么我能帮你的吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "No."
msgstr "没有。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid ""
"If you're willing to help us, ask the other guard by the entrance. He might "
"need your assistance in dealing with labor and stuff."
msgstr "如果你愿意帮忙，去问问入口处的另一个守卫。他可能需要你协助处理些劳力之类的活儿。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "See ya then!"
msgstr "那回头见！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "I'm just a guard, I have no problems with my position."
msgstr "我只是个守卫，对自己的职位没什么不满。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg1_responses.json
msgid "The commando has sent me here."
msgstr "是突击队派我来的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "What do you seek?"
msgstr "你在寻找什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "What do you want?"
msgstr "你想要什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "What are you looking for?"
msgstr "你在找什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Just come in..."
msgstr "直接进来吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Let's talk for a moment."
msgstr "我们聊一会儿。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I want to talk with you..."
msgstr "我想和你谈谈……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I guess you're important. What is it?"
msgstr "我猜你挺重要的。什么事？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "No..."
msgstr "不……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "No!"
msgstr "不！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "The guard told me you need my help."
msgstr "守卫告诉我你需要帮助。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "How's the life here?"
msgstr "这里的生活怎么样？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "About that job..."
msgstr "关于那份工作……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Something I need to do?"
msgstr "有什么需要我做的吗？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I better get going..."
msgstr "我最好还是走吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "You're at the wasteland outskirts, now move, mortal."
msgstr "你已在废土边缘，现在动身吧，凡人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Wait. I want to know more about the places you know..."
msgstr "等等。我想多了解些你知道的地方……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay, I'll move."
msgstr "好吧，我这就走。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Like what?"
msgstr "比如什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "About HIM's location?"
msgstr "关于“他”的位置？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Actually, nevermind..."
msgstr "其实，算了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"I know you've been told its a deep secret, but why do you mind about our "
"master?"
msgstr "我知道你被告知这是绝密，但为何在意我们的主人？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I'd like to meet HIM."
msgstr "我想见“他”。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "HE looks questionable."
msgstr "“他”看起来可疑。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I want to know HIS upcoming actions."
msgstr "我想知道“他”接下来的行动。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Forget it..."
msgstr "忘了吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "In which will never happen to a human."
msgstr "这永远不会发生在人类身上。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I guess I've talked about everything..."
msgstr "我想该说的都说了……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid " That sucks..."
msgstr "真糟糕……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I know. HE's full of mysteries even me can't talk about."
msgstr "我知道。“他”充满谜团，连我也无法多谈。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Trust me, human, HIS movements are for the good cause."
msgstr "相信我，人类，“他”的举动是为了崇高的目标。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Oh, okay then..."
msgstr "哦，那好吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"Don't worry, mortal. Eventually, you'll meet someone to quench your thirst "
"for deeper answers."
msgstr "别担心，凡人。终有一天，你会遇到能解你更深层答案之渴的人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Uhh, okay..."
msgstr "呃，好吧……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Uhh, okay... I'll expect that."
msgstr "呃，好吧……我会期待的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"Nah, I'm just a guard here doing my job. If you want to know more, seek the "
"guard in the kitchen."
msgstr "不，我只是个在这儿干活的守卫。想了解更多的话，去找厨房里的守卫吧。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "He told me to help you with something."
msgstr "他让我来帮你处理些事情。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Okay, I'm going..."
msgstr "好的，我这就去……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"So you're interested in helping us out with our problems... But I don't want"
" to get you in trouble."
msgstr "看来你有兴趣帮我们解决问题……但我不想给你惹麻烦。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I'll take the risk!"
msgstr "我愿意冒这个险！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Forget it, I'm out of that!"
msgstr "算了，我不掺和了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "If you insist..."
msgstr "如果你坚持的话……"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"We've got some cows here as our food source and a water nearby for humans to"
" quench their thirst."
msgstr "我们这儿有些牛作为食物来源，附近还有水源供人类解渴。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "I mean what are you vampires drinking?"
msgstr "我是说你们吸血鬼喝什么？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid "Cows? Where'd you get them?"
msgstr "牛？你们从哪儿弄来的？"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"Blood, ofcourse! We drink blood from the cows as our substitute to human's. "
"Don't worry about the refugees here, we tend to protect them as ordered."
msgstr "当然是血！我们喝牛血作为人血的替代品。别担心这里的难民，我们奉命保护他们。"

#: .\Modification_Files\NPC\v_npc_responds\Wastelands_Outskirts\v_wg2_responses.json
msgid ""
"We herd them from the wilderness. We don't know if they came from the "
"nearest farm, but certainly they are free from infection."
msgstr "我们从荒野中放牧它们。不清楚是否来自最近的农场，但肯定没有感染。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Others\v_dialogue_effects.json
msgid "Unsealing"
msgstr "解封中"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Unsealing'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Others\v_dialogue_effects.json
msgid "The vampire is currently breaking the seal."
msgstr "吸血鬼正在破除封印。"

