#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks Of The Blood, Vol. 1"
msgid_plural "Magicks Of The Blood, Vol. 1s"
msgstr[0] "鲜血魔法，第一卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks Of The Blood, Vol. 1'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate brass embelshements"
" in unsettling abstract designs. The contents focus on the basics of "
"Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation."
msgstr "这本书以红棕色皮革装订，饰有令人不安的抽象图案的华丽黄铜装饰。内容聚焦于鲜血魔法的基础，这是一种声名狼藉的血腥技艺。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 2"
msgid_plural "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 2s"
msgstr[0] "鲜血魔法，第二卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 2'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate bronze "
"embelshements in unsettling abstract designs. The contents focus on "
"Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation. These spells are more "
"advanced than the first volume."
msgstr "这本书以红棕色皮革装订，饰有令人不安的抽象图案的华丽青铜装饰。内容聚焦于鲜血魔法，这是一种声名狼藉的血腥技艺。其中的法术比第一卷更为高级。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 3"
msgid_plural "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 3s"
msgstr[0] "鲜血魔法，第三卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 3'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate copper "
"embelshements in unsettling abstract designs. The contents focus on "
"Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation. This work is directed at a "
"more experienced blood magician."
msgstr "这本书以红棕色皮革装订，饰有令人不安的抽象图案的华丽铜饰。内容聚焦于鲜血魔法，这是一种声名狼藉的血腥技艺。这部作品面向更有经验的鲜血法师。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 4"
msgid_plural "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 4s"
msgstr[0] "鲜血魔法，第四卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 4'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate silver "
"embelshements in unsettling abstract designs. The contents focus on "
"Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation. The spells herein are "
"intended for veteran blood magickers."
msgstr ""
"这本书以红棕色皮革装订，饰有令人不安的抽象图案的华丽银饰。内容聚焦于鲜血魔法，这是一种声名狼藉的血腥技艺。其中的法术专为资深的鲜血法师设计。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 5"
msgid_plural "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 5s"
msgstr[0] "鲜血魔法，第五卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 5'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate golden "
"embelshements in unsettling abstract designs. The contents focus on "
"Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation. The spells herein are most "
"useful to an elder blood magus."
msgstr ""
"这本书以红棕色皮革装订，饰有令人不安的抽象图案的华丽金饰。内容聚焦于鲜血魔法，这是一种声名狼藉的血腥技艺。其中的法术对年长的鲜血大师最为有用。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 6"
msgid_plural "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 6s"
msgstr[0] "鲜血魔法，第六卷"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 6'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate platinum "
"embelshements in unsettling abstract designs. The contents focus on "
"Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation. This work is aimed at those "
"on the cusp of mastery of blood."
msgstr ""
"这本书以红褐色皮革装订，饰有华丽铂金浮雕，图案为令人不安的抽象设计。内容聚焦于血魔法，这是一门声名狼藉的血腥技艺。本书面向那些即将精通血液奥秘之人。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 7"
msgid_plural "Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 7s"
msgstr[0] "《鲜血魔典·卷七》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Magicks of the Blood, Vol. 7'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in reddish-brown leather, with ornate embelshements "
"forged of slick red blood-infused steel in unsettling abstract designs. The "
"contents focus on Hemomancy, a bloody art with a dark reputation. The final "
"secrets of arch-magi of the sanguine arts are contained herein."
msgstr ""
"这本书以红褐色皮革装订，饰有华丽浮雕，由光滑的渗血红钢锻造而成，图案为令人不安的抽象设计。内容聚焦于血魔法，这是一门声名狼藉的血腥技艺。其中蕴藏着血艺大法师的终极奥秘。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "To Embrace The Tainted Elements"
msgid_plural "To Embrace The Tainted Elementss"
msgstr[0] "《拥抱污秽元素》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'To Embrace The Tainted Elements'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is sturdy, with a thin crimson-hued leather binding over metal "
"cover plates and a steel spine. Within are lessons in the basics of Profane "
"Conjuration."
msgstr "这本书结构坚固，采用薄薄的深红色皮革包裹金属封面和钢制书脊。内页记载了亵渎召唤术的基础教程。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "To Call Down Cursed Flame"
msgid_plural "To Call Down Cursed Flames"
msgstr[0] "《唤来诅咒之焰》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'To Call Down Cursed Flame'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"Scarred steel plates bind this thin tome. Within, more Profane Conjuration "
"secrets await."
msgstr "这本薄册以带疤痕的钢板装订。内页隐藏着更多亵渎召唤术的秘密。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "To War With Frost And Cinder"
msgid_plural "To War With Frost And Cinders"
msgstr[0] "《与寒霜余烬为战》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'To War With Frost And Cinder'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"Thick furs and leathers gird this book. The spells within are intermediate "
"Profane Conjuration workings."
msgstr "这本书以厚实的毛皮和皮革包裹。其中的法术属于亵渎召唤术的中阶运用。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "To Seal The Path With Fire"
msgid_plural "To Seal The Path With Fires"
msgstr[0] "《以火封途》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'To Seal The Path With Fire'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This book is bound in fire-blackened wood and curiously undecayed rawhide. "
"It has some Profane Conjuration knowledge within, but you have to sort "
"through a lot of bad poetry to get it."
msgstr "这本书以烧焦的木材和奇异未腐的生皮装订。其中包含一些亵渎召唤术的知识，但你需要从大量拙劣的诗句中筛选出来。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "To Dance With Inferno And Blizzard"
msgid_plural "To Dance With Inferno And Blizzards"
msgstr[0] "《与地狱火与暴风雪共舞》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'To Dance With Inferno And Blizzard'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"A simple but curiously durable parchment cover adorns this book. The Profane"
" Conjuration spells here are very advanced, and focus on hard-hitting "
"offense."
msgstr "这本书以简单却异常耐用的羊皮纸封面装饰。其中的亵渎召唤术咒语极为高深，专注于强力的攻击手段。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "The Heights Of Blaze And Chill"
msgid_plural "The Heights Of Blaze And Chills"
msgstr[0] "《烈焰与寒霜之巅》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'The Heights Of Blaze And Chill'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"Robust leather binding over beautifully illuminated pages, this work of "
"Profane Conjuration speaks to experts of its art."
msgstr "这本书采用坚固的皮革装订，内页饰有精美的彩绘，这部亵渎召唤术著作专为精通此道的专家而作。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "On Conjuring The Profane"
msgid_plural "On Conjuring The Profanes"
msgstr[0] "《论亵渎召唤》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'On Conjuring The Profane'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"A plain book, so nondescript you almost thought it was an encyclopedia. The "
"printing is clean and modern, and the language is clear and lacks the "
"flowery scope of prior works. It lays out, in no uncertain terms, the spells"
" available to the height of Profane Conjuration's students."
msgstr ""
"一本朴素的书，平凡得几乎让人误以为是百科全书。印刷清晰现代，语言简洁明了，没有早期作品的华丽辞藻。它毫不含糊地列出了亵渎召唤术高阶学徒可用的法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Scrawled Notebook"
msgid_plural "Scrawled Notebooks"
msgstr[0] "《潦草笔记》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Scrawled Notebook'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"A normal looking composition notebook with multiple odd stains and hints of "
"curious scents about it. Scrawled within are basic spells for the magical "
"discipline identified with its practicioners, the Warlock."
msgstr "一本外观普通的作文本，有多处奇怪的污渍和隐约的奇特气味。内页潦草地记载着与其实践者——术士——相关的魔法学科基础咒语。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Battered Binder"
msgid_plural "Battered Binders"
msgstr[0] "《破旧活页夹》"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Battered Binder'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This old binder could have stepped off the set of a 1960s period drama. The "
"contents are crazily scrawled pages outlining spells for a neophyte Warlock."
msgstr "这本旧活页夹仿佛刚从1960年代的古装剧片场走出来。里面是疯狂涂写的页面，概述了新手术士的法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Well-Traveled Portfolio"
msgid_plural "Well-Traveled Portfolios"
msgstr[0] "阅历丰富的文件夹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Well-Traveled Portfolio'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This worn leather folio smells faintly of iron and a musty hint of decay. "
"Within are multiple pages outlining spells and incantations for the adept "
"Warlock, mostly discovered via experimentation."
msgstr "这个磨损的皮革文件夹散发着淡淡的铁锈味和一丝霉腐气息。里面有多页内容，概述了熟练术士的法术与咒语，大多是通过实验发现的。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Tattered Pamphlet"
msgid_plural "Tattered Pamphlets"
msgstr[0] "破旧的小册子"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tattered Pamphlet'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"A small chapbook-sized comic that you would normally expect to see "
"proclaiming a reactionary religious position, but this one is much "
"different. It discusses magic available to a more experienced Warlock."
msgstr "一本小册子大小的漫画，通常你会以为它宣扬的是反动宗教立场，但这本却大不相同。它讨论了经验更丰富的术士可用的魔法。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Traveller's Journal"
msgid_plural "Traveller's Journals"
msgstr[0] "旅行者日记"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Traveller's Journal"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This is a journal not unlike those you could pick up at your local "
"bookstore. The handwriting is neat, and in between sketches of various "
"leeches, bats, and sanguine horrors the author provides several expert "
"Warlock spells."
msgstr "这本日记与你可以在当地书店买到的那种没什么两样。字迹工整，在各种水蛭、蝙蝠和血腥恐怖的素描之间，作者提供了几个专家级术士法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Student's Folder"
msgid_plural "Student's Folders"
msgstr[0] "学生文件夹"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Student's Folder"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"A plain rust-brown colored folder, you could find its like in any big-box "
"store. The papers herein discuss highly advanced Warlock magicks."
msgstr "一个朴素的铁锈棕色文件夹，你在任何大型商店都能找到类似的东西。里面的纸张讨论了高度高级的术士魔法。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid "Brightly Colored Trap Keeper"
msgid_plural "Brightly Colored Trap Keepers"
msgstr[0] "色彩鲜艳的陷阱守护者"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Brightly Colored Trap Keeper'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\spellbooks.json
msgid ""
"This binder looks like someone threw up Skittles all over it. Laden in neon "
"colors, a bright cartoon bat proclaims 'EVERYTHING SUCKS' from the center of"
" the frontplate. Ironic, as this binder has the highest secrets of the "
"Warlock within."
msgstr ""
"这个活页夹看起来像是有人把彩虹糖吐满了它。满载霓虹色彩，一个鲜艳的卡通蝙蝠在前板中央宣告着“一切都很烂”。讽刺的是，这个活页夹内藏着术士的最高秘密。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Tranfusion Spell"
msgstr "输血法术"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tranfusion Spell'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "It will cast Transfusion Damage and Transfusion Heal."
msgstr "它将施放输血伤害和输血治疗。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Tranfusion Spell'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "You feel refreshed as you cast!"
msgstr "施法时你感到神清气爽！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Tranfusion Heal"
msgstr "输血治疗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tranfusion Heal'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Heals the caster with 1 hp."
msgstr "治疗施法者1点生命值。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Tranfusion Damage"
msgstr "输血伤害"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Tranfusion Damage'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Damages the target with 2 hp."
msgstr "对目标造成2点生命值伤害。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Crimson Haze Blind"
msgstr "深红迷雾致盲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Crimson Haze Blind'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Blind foes within a 4 tile radius."
msgstr "使4格半径内的敌人失明。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Outrage Bash"
msgstr "狂怒猛击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Outrage Bash'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Deals 25 bash damage."
msgstr "造成25点钝击伤害。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Outrage Bash'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "An ourburst of thick tentacle slaps!"
msgstr "一阵粗壮触须的猛烈拍打！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Outrage Cut"
msgstr "狂怒斩击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Outrage Cut'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Deals 25 cut damage."
msgstr "造成25点切割伤害。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Outrage Cut'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "A tentacle strand slashes!"
msgstr "一束触须猛然挥砍！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Outrage Stab"
msgstr "狂怒刺击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Outrage Stab'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Deals 25 stab damage."
msgstr "造成25点穿刺伤害。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Outrage Stab'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "A tendril bursts then thrusts!"
msgstr "一根卷须爆裂并突刺！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Outrage Drain"
msgstr "狂怒汲取"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Outrage Drain'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "It will cast Drain Damage and Drain Heal."
msgstr "它将施放汲取伤害与汲取治疗。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Outrage Drain'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "You suddenly feel refreshed!"
msgstr "你突然感到精神焕发！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_hit_time.json
msgid "Drain Heal"
msgstr "汲取治疗"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Drain Heal'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Heals the caster with 5 hp."
msgstr "为施法者恢复5点生命值。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_hit_time.json
msgid "Drain Damage"
msgstr "汲取伤害"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Drain Damage'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Damages the target with 10 hp."
msgstr "对目标造成10点生命值伤害。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Dark Burst Push"
msgstr "暗影爆发推击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dark Burst Push'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Push monsters within a 4 tile radius."
msgstr "推开4格范围内的怪物。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Megamagic Exhaust?"
msgstr "超魔耗竭？"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Megamagic Exhaust?'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "1/4 chance to do Megamagic Exhaust."
msgstr "有1/4的几率触发超魔耗竭。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Megamagic Exhaust!"
msgstr "超级魔法耗竭！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Megamagic Exhaust!'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Does the Megamagic Exhaust."
msgstr "造成超级魔法耗竭。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Megamagic Exhaust"
msgstr "超级魔法耗竭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Megamagic Exhaust'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Weakens the player."
msgstr "削弱玩家。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Exhaustion"
msgstr "耗竭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Exhaustion'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Depletes the stamina."
msgstr "消耗耐力。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Dark Pillar Bash"
msgstr "暗黑柱击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dark Pillar Bash'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_combo.json
msgid "Aims to make a crater under the target. If not, then don't."
msgstr "旨在目标下方制造一个坑洞。若未成功，则不会。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Blood Curled"
msgstr "血液凝固"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Blood Curled'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "You feel yourself very stiff."
msgstr "你感到自己非常僵硬。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Clotting"
msgstr "凝血"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Clotting'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Blood clots are actively seeking for bleeding body parts to repair."
msgstr "血块正积极寻找出血的身体部位进行修复。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Ensnared"
msgstr "被束缚"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Ensnared'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Viscous blood sticks to your body!"
msgstr "粘稠的血液附着在你身上！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Crimson Hazed"
msgstr "深红迷雾"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Crimson Hazed'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Sticky vapors of blood takes a firm hold of your body!"
msgstr "血液的粘稠蒸汽牢牢抓住了你的身体！"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Blood Surge'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Surge of blood flows through your vessel!"
msgstr "血液涌动流经你的血管！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Withering"
msgstr "凋零"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Withering'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Pressence of a vile aura drains you submissively!"
msgstr "邪恶光环的存在让你被动地流失精力！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Binded"
msgstr "束缚"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Binded'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "You can't even move an inch."
msgstr "你甚至无法移动分毫。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Ethereal Grasp"
msgstr "以太之握"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Ethereal Grasp'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "You're held by an etherean silhouette."
msgstr "你被一道以太虚影所束缚。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T3.json
msgid "Mana Surge"
msgstr "魔力涌动"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Mana Surge'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Unholy surge of mana flows through you!"
msgstr "一股不洁的魔力洪流在你体内奔涌！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Exhausted"
msgstr "精疲力竭"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Exhausted'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "That blast really packs a punch!"
msgstr "这一击威力十足！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Ethereal Shock"
msgstr "以太冲击"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Ethereal Shock'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "You've seen alot of things. Now you suffer from it!"
msgstr "你见识过太多事物，如今正为此承受苦果！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Doomed"
msgstr "厄运缠身"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Doomed'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "The glowing marks around your body doesn't seem to be friendly..."
msgstr "你身上发光的印记似乎并不友善……"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "On Fire"
msgstr "着火"

#. ~ Description of effect 'On Fire'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid ""
"Loss of health - Entire Body\n"
"Your clothing and other equipment may be consumed by the flames."
msgstr ""
"生命值流失 - 全身\n"
"你的衣物和其他装备可能被火焰吞噬。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Hit by Player"
msgstr "被玩家击中"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Hit by Player'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid ""
"AI tag for when monsters are hit by player. This is a bug if you have it."
msgstr "怪物被玩家击中时的AI标签。如果你有此状态，说明出现了错误。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Cursed"
msgstr "诅咒"

#. ~ Description of effect 'Cursed'.
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "You take more elemental damage!"
msgstr "你受到的元素伤害增加了！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\v_spell_effects.json
msgid "Freezed"
msgstr "冻结"

