#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid "leech's whip"
msgid_plural "leech's whips"
msgstr[0] "吸血鞭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "leech's whip"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid ""
"Viscious dire whip, serving its owner with an unbreakable loyalty. Throbs as if it is alive, its bloodlust flows through its wielder who radiates in faint, velvety aura.\n"
"* 10% chance to perform Sweeping Strike while attacking. Sweeping Strike deals <color_light_red>16 cutting damage</color> to foes in a very wide cone.\n"
"* 20% chance to drain life force from an adjacent foe when hit, dealing up to <color_green>2 biological damage</color> and heals you by <color_green>1</color>."
msgstr ""
"凶残的恐怖长鞭，以坚不可摧的忠诚侍奉其主。脉动如活物，其嗜血渴望流经持有者，散发出微弱的天鹅绒般光晕。\n"
"* 攻击时有10%概率发动横扫打击。横扫打击对极宽锥形范围内的敌人造成<color_light_red>16点切割伤害</color>。\n"
"* 击中时有20%概率从相邻敌人吸取生命精华，造成最多<color_green>2点生物伤害</color>并为你恢复<color_green>1点</color>生命。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid "crimson coat"
msgid_plural "crimson coats"
msgstr[0] "猩红血衣"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'crimson coat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid ""
"A thick layer of blood, protecting your body from harm. 'Break' the barrier by dropping it.\n"
"* 75% chance for the coat to react, immediately piercing the attacker when hit that deals <color_green>12 stabbing damage</color> and renders them <color_yellow>unconscious</color> for 1-3 turns."
msgstr ""
"一层厚重的血液，保护身体免受伤害。通过丢弃可“打破”此屏障。\n"
"* 被击中时血衣有75%概率反应，立即刺穿攻击者，造成<color_green>12点穿刺伤害</color>并使其<color_yellow>昏迷</color>1-3回合。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid "<color_red>Orus</color>"
msgid_plural "<color_red>Orus</color>s"
msgstr[0] "<color_red>奥鲁斯</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': '<color_red>Orus</color>'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid ""
"Hemomancer form:\n"
"<color_red>Orus</color>, the zealous manipulator.\n"
"* 10% chance to summon a <color_light_blue>bloodling</color> near a blood field within 10 tiles for every 20 seconds.\n"
"* 10% chance to summon a <color_light_blue>bloodling</color> when hit.\n"
"* 20% chance to summon a <color_light_blue>bloodling</color> and 5% chance to summon a <color_light_blue>bloodling predecessor</color> while attacking."
msgstr ""
"血法师形态：\n"
"<color_red>奥鲁斯</color>，狂热的操纵者。\n"
"* 每20秒有10%概率在10格内的血域附近召唤一只<color_light_blue>血裔</color>。\n"
"* 被击中时有10%概率召唤一只<color_light_blue>血裔</color>。\n"
"* 攻击时有20%概率召唤一只<color_light_blue>血裔</color>，5%概率召唤一只<color_light_blue>血裔先祖</color>。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid "ethereal enchantment"
msgid_plural "ethereal enchantments"
msgstr[0] "以太附魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ethereal enchantment'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_item.json
msgid ""
"Enshrouds your wielded weapon (or even bare fists) in ghastly mists.\n"
"* 5% to summon an <color_light_blue>etherean silhouette</color> for 15-25 turns while attacking."
msgstr ""
"用幽灵般的迷雾笼罩你持有的武器（甚至空拳）。\n"
"* 攻击时有5%概率召唤一个<color_light_blue>以太幻影</color>，持续15-25回合。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "desolate gloom"
msgid_plural "desolate glooms"
msgstr[0] "荒芜幽影"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'desolate gloom'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "A hovering mist of pure dread, undulating in soft, patterned beats."
msgstr "一团纯粹恐惧的悬浮迷雾，以柔和、有节奏的脉动起伏。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "bloodling"
msgid_plural "bloodlings"
msgstr[0] "血裔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'bloodling'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "Bloated lump of blood, forming into something... frightening."
msgstr "肿胀的血块，正逐渐形成某种……令人恐惧的东西。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "etherean silhouette"
msgid_plural "etherean silhouettes"
msgstr[0] "虚灵魅影"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'etherean silhouette'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "A deceitful humanoid shadow, glimmering in faint, ghastly light."
msgstr "一道诡诈的人形阴影，在微弱而惨淡的光线中若隐若现。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'etherean silhouette'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
#, c-format
msgid "%1$s stares at %3$s as it gesture its arms!"
msgstr "%1$s 凝视着 %3$s，同时挥舞着手臂！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "Vex"
msgid_plural "Vexs"
msgstr[0] "维克斯"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vex'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid ""
"An etherean deity, concealed beneath an impenetrable barrier. Within a clear"
" vision, a vaguely humanoid figure floats freely mid-air."
msgstr "一位虚灵神祇，隐匿于无法穿透的屏障之下。在清晰的视野中，一个模糊的人形身影自由地悬浮在半空中。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'Vex'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
#, c-format
msgid "%1$s shimmers as it glares at %3$s!"
msgstr "%1$s 闪烁着微光，怒视着 %3$s！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid "ethereal harbringer"
msgid_plural "ethereal harbringers"
msgstr[0] "虚灵先驱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'ethereal harbringer'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
msgid ""
"A ghastly cloud of concentrated etherean power. Seems to be volatile, and "
"may suddenly implode when it is touched."
msgstr "一团浓缩虚灵之力的恐怖云团。似乎极不稳定，被触碰时可能会突然内爆。"

#. ~ Attack message of monster "{'str': 'ethereal harbringer'}"'s spell "None"
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\+Misc\v_spell_mon.json
#, c-format
msgid "%1$s shines vigorously!"
msgstr "%1$s 剧烈地闪耀着！"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Transfusion'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T1.json
msgid ""
"The basic spell of a hemomancer, draining a random hostile's life force within reach.\n"
"* For every damage, it deals up to <color_green>2 biological damage</color> and heals you by <color_green>1</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"血法师的基础法术，吸取范围内随机敌对目标的生机。\n"
"* 每次造成伤害时，最多造成 <color_green>2 点生物伤害</color>，并为你恢复 <color_green>1</color> 点生命值。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个 <color_light_gray>1 阶</color> 法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T1.json
msgid "Blood Curl"
msgstr "血之卷曲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Curl'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T1.json
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>Immobilizes</color> the target by manipulating its life force to bind onto itself.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"通过操纵目标的生机使其束缚自身，从而 <color_yellow>定身</color> 目标。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个 <color_light_gray>1 阶</color> 法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T1.json
msgid "Clot"
msgstr "凝血术"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Clot'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T1.json
msgid ""
"You use your blood to send towards the <color_yellow>bleeding</color> body part and mend it immediately. While active, it'll block further <color_yellow>bleeding</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"你用自己的血液涌向 <color_yellow>流血</color> 的肢体部位，并立即将其治愈。激活期间，它将阻止进一步的 <color_yellow>流血</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个 <color_light_gray>1 阶</color> 法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T2.json
msgid "Blood Puddle"
msgstr "血泊术"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Puddle'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T2.json
msgid ""
"You barf a mouthful of thick blood in an area, greatly slowing any creature that walks through it.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 2</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"你在区域内呕出一大口浓稠血液，大幅减缓任何穿行其间的生物。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个 <color_light_gray>2 阶</color> 法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T2.json
msgid "Blood Sting"
msgstr "血刺术"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Sting'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T2.json
msgid ""
"Conjure own's blood to shoot towards the target, shaping into a dart as it fly that deals <color_light_red>stabbing damage</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 2</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"凝聚自身的血液射向目标，飞行过程中化作一枚飞镖，造成 <color_light_red>穿刺伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个 <color_light_gray>2 阶</color> 法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T3.json
msgid "Crimson Haze"
msgstr "猩红迷雾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Crimson Haze'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T3.json
msgid ""
"Vaporizes your blood to create a disorienting wave of haze that <color_yellow>slows down</color> foes around you.\n"
"* Foes within a 4 tile radius are afflicted with <color_yellow>blindness</color> for 7 turns.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_white>Tier 3</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"蒸发你的血液，制造一片令人迷失的迷雾波，使周围的敌人<color_yellow>减速</color>。\n"
"* 半径4格内的敌人将遭受<color_yellow>失明</color>效果，持续7回合。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_white>第3阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T3.json
msgid "Suppress"
msgstr "压制"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Suppress'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T3.json
msgid ""
"Heavily binds the target, dealing <color_green>biological damage</color> and renders them <color_yellow>unconscious</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_white>Tier 3</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"严重束缚目标，造成<color_green>生物伤害</color>并使其<color_yellow>昏迷</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_white>第3阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T4.json
msgid "Riptide"
msgstr "激流"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Riptide'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T4.json
msgid ""
"Conjures a large amount of blood to strike the targets inside a wide cone, dealing <color_magenta>bashing damage</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_red>tier 4</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"召唤大量血液，攻击宽锥形范围内的目标，造成<color_magenta>钝击伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_red>第4阶</color>法术。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Surge'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T4.json
msgid ""
"You put yourself in a <color_yellow>battle trance</color> using your life force, increasing your might, mobility and endurance for a short period of time.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_red>tier 4</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"你利用生命力使自己进入<color_yellow>战斗狂怒</color>状态，短时间内提升力量、机动性和耐力。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_red>第4阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T4.json
msgid "Blood Wave"
msgstr "血浪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blood Wave'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T4.json
msgid ""
"An innate flash flood of blood bursts out from you, dealing <color_magenta>bashing damage</color> to the surrounding targets.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_red>tier 4</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"一股与生俱来的血液洪流从你体内爆发，对周围目标造成<color_magenta>钝击伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_red>第4阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T5.json
msgid "Vampiric Outrage"
msgstr "吸血鬼之怒"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Vampiric Outrage'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T5.json
msgid ""
"Sets you in catastrophic madness, consuming own's life force in exchange of barraging random attacks.\n"
"* For every damage, you randomly attack foes with 25 (<color_magenta>bash</color>, cut or <color_light_red>stab</color>) damage within a 12 tile radius. There's a 1/10 chance to suck the target's life force, dealing up to <color_green>10 biological damage</color> and heals you by <color_green>5</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_red>tier 5</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"使你陷入灾难性的疯狂，消耗自身生命力以换取随机攻击的狂潮。\n"
"* 每次造成伤害时，你会在半径12格内随机攻击敌人，造成25点（<color_magenta>钝击</color>、切割或<color_light_red>穿刺</color>）伤害。有1/10的几率吸取目标生命力，造成最多<color_green>10点生物伤害</color>并为你恢复<color_green>5点</color>生命。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_red>第5阶</color>法术。"

#. ~ Message for SPELL '{'str': 'Vampiric Outrage'}'
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T5.json
msgid ""
"<color_light_red>Dread fills your mind and body...</color>\n"
"As you stand, blood tendrils emerges from you!"
msgstr ""
"<color_light_red>恐惧充斥你的身心...</color>\n"
"当你站立时，血液触须从你身上涌现！"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T5.json
msgid "Essence Pull"
msgstr "精华汲取"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Essence Pull'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T5.json
msgid ""
"Attempts to instantly kill the target by draining every ounce of their life force, dealing immensive <color_green>biological damage</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_red>tier 5</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"试图通过吸干目标的每一丝生命力来立即杀死目标，造成巨大的<color_green>生物伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_red>第5阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T6.json
msgid "Desolation"
msgstr "荒芜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Desolation'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T6.json
msgid ""
"Sacrifices a massive amount of life force to summon a <color_brown>lingering aura</color> that <color_yellow>saps life</color> from all surrounding creatures, dealing constant <color_green>biological damage</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"牺牲大量生命力，召唤一个<color_brown>持续存在的灵气</color>，从所有周围生物身上<color_yellow>汲取生命</color>，造成持续的<color_green>生物伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>第6阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T6.json
msgid "Crimson Coat"
msgstr "猩红之甲"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Crimson Coat'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T6.json
msgid ""
"You withdraw for a very short moment, covering your whole body with <color_brown>thick blood layer</color> that nullifies most physical damage. This thick layer does not burden you in any way.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"你短暂后撤，用<color_brown>厚实的血液层</color>覆盖全身，抵消大部分物理伤害。这层厚实的血液层不会对你造成任何负担。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>第6阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T6.json
msgid "Leech's Whip"
msgstr "水蛭之鞭"

#. ~ Description for {'str': "Leech's Whip"}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T6.json
msgid ""
"Summons the <color_brown>leech's whip</color>, a biological melee weapon.\n"
"* If wielded while active, provides positives flat bonuses to stats (STR +1, SPD +5) and increases your maximum health by 10.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"召唤<color_brown>水蛭之鞭</color>，一种生物近战武器。\n"
"* 激活时若持有，提供属性正面固定加成（力量+1，速度+5），并增加10点最大生命值。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>第6阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T7.json
msgid "Form: <color_red>Orus</color>"
msgstr "形态：<color_red>奥鲁斯</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Form: <color_red>Orus</color>'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Hemomancer\v_blood_T7.json
msgid ""
"Impersonates one of ancient hemomancers - Orus, the zealous manipulator - who possesses the ability to rise the impure beings from the blood of their victim.\n"
"* While actively 'having' this form, gains a negative flat bonus to stat (SPD -15), but increases your maximum health by 50.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_pink>tier 7</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"模仿古代血法师之一——奥鲁斯，这位狂热的操纵者——他拥有从受害者血液中唤起不洁生物的能力。\n"
"* 在主动“拥有”此形态时，获得属性负面固定加成（速度-15），但增加50点最大生命值。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_pink>第7阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T1.json
msgid "Exerxium"
msgstr "埃克瑟西姆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Exerxium'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T1.json
msgid ""
"Ignites the foe with ardent profane blaze, dealing <color_red>fire damage</color> and <color_yellow>curses</color> them.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"以炽热亵渎之焰点燃敌人，造成<color_red>火焰伤害</color>并<color_yellow>诅咒</color>他们。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_gray>1阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T1.json
msgid "Frost"
msgstr "寒霜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Frost'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T1.json
msgid ""
"Binds the foe by instantly converting the air into ice, dealing <color_white>cold damage</color> and <color_yellow>freezes</color> them.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"瞬间将空气转化为冰束缚敌人，造成<color_white>寒冷伤害</color>并<color_yellow>冻结</color>他们。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_gray>1阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T1.json
msgid "Elemental Dissipation"
msgstr "元素消散"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Elemental Dissipation'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T1.json
msgid ""
"Nullifies <color_yellow>elemental blights</color> from you or an ally.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"消除你或盟友身上的<color_yellow>元素侵蚀</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_gray>1阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T2.json
msgid "Ignite"
msgstr "点燃"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ignite'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T2.json
msgid ""
"Sets foe <color_yellow>ablaze</color>, dealing <color_red>fire damage</color.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 2</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"使敌人<color_yellow>燃烧</color>，造成<color_red>火焰伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_gray>2阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T3.json
msgid "Perfury"
msgstr "珀弗瑞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Perfury'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T3.json
msgid ""
"Conjures dark, hellish flames to engulf the foe, dealing <color_red>fire damage</color> and is afflicted with <color_yellow>cursed flames</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_white>tier 3</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"召唤黑暗地狱之火吞噬敌人，造成<color_red>火焰伤害</color>并使其遭受<color_yellow>诅咒火焰</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_white>3阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T3.json
msgid "Blizzaga"
msgstr "暴雪"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Blizzaga'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T3.json
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>Immobilizes</color> the foe by flash-freezing the air around them, dealing <color_white>cold damage</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_white>tier 3</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"通过瞬间冻结敌人周围的空气<color_yellow>定身</color>敌人，造成<color_white>寒冷伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_white>3阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T4.json
msgid "Fire Wall"
msgstr "火墙"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Fire Wall'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T4.json
msgid ""
"Surrounds the foe inside a blazing wall of flames.\n"
"* Creates fire fields outside the aoe range.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_red>tier 4</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"用烈焰之墙将敌人包围其中。\n"
"* 在作用范围外创造火焰区域。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_red>4阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T5.json
msgid "Firebane"
msgstr "炎祸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Firebane'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T5.json
msgid ""
"Conjures a profane fireball to strike the foe. Upon impact, it explodes, dealing <color_red>fire damage</color> and spreads cursed flames on that area.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_red>tier 5</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"召唤亵渎火球打击敌人。命中时爆炸，造成<color_red>火焰伤害</color>并在该区域扩散诅咒火焰。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_red>5阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T5.json
msgid "Icebane"
msgstr "冰祸"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Icebane'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T5.json
msgid ""
"Conjures a profane ball of fiery ice to strike the foe. Upon impact, it shatters, dealing <color_white>cold damage</color> and spreads frostburn on that area.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_red>tier 5</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"召唤亵渎的炽热冰球打击敌人。命中时碎裂，造成<color_white>寒冷伤害</color>并在该区域扩散霜燃。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_red>5阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T6.json
msgid "Deus Exerxium"
msgstr "神之埃克瑟西姆"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Deus Exerxium'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T6.json
msgid ""
"A wave of profane blaze strikes all foes within a cone, dealing <color_red>fire damage</color> and <color_yellow>curses</color> them.\n"
"* Slim chance to spread cursed flames on the affected area.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"亵渎之焰的波浪冲击锥形范围内的所有敌人，造成<color_red>火焰伤害</color>并<color_yellow>诅咒</color>他们。\n"
"* 有微小几率在受影响区域扩散诅咒火焰。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>6阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T6.json
msgid "Elemental Ward"
msgstr "元素护盾"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Elemental Ward'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T6.json
msgid ""
"Creates a barrier that protects you or an ally from all <color_yellow>elemental blights</color>.\n"
"* Doesn't nullify existing <color_yellow>blights</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"创造一个屏障，保护你或盟友免受所有<color_yellow>元素侵蚀</color>。\n"
"* 不会消除现有的<color_yellow>侵蚀</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>6阶</color>法术。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Desecrate'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T7.json
msgid ""
"Channels the underworld to create a rift that engulfs the foe with a towering hellfire, dealing massive <color_red>fire damage</color>, inflicts a long-lasting <color_yellow>curse</color> and leaves an intense cursed flame at that point.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_pink>tier 7</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"引导冥界之力，创造一个裂隙，用冲天业火吞噬敌人，造成大量<color_red>火焰伤害</color>，施加一个持久的<color_yellow>诅咒</color>，并在该处留下强烈的诅咒火焰。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_pink>7阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T7.json
msgid "Eternal Frost"
msgstr "永恒冰霜"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Eternal Frost'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Profane_Conjurer\v_elem_T7.json
msgid ""
"A blast of sheer wind <color_yellow>flash-freezes</color> all creatures in an area, dealing <color_white>cold damage</color>.\n"
"* Creates a lingering frost fields that freezes any creature that comes in contact.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_pink>tier 7</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"一阵纯粹的风<color_yellow>瞬间冻结</color>区域内所有生物，造成<color_white>寒冷伤害</color>。\n"
"* 创造一个持续的冰霜领域，冻结任何接触的生物。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_pink>7阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T1.json
msgid "Arcane Binding"
msgstr "奥术束缚"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Arcane Binding'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T1.json
msgid ""
"Hits your foe with your weapon imbued in etherean arcane binding, striking its inner self that deals <color_light_gray>pure damage</color> and <color_yellow>immobilizes</color> them.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"用灌注以太奥术束缚的武器击中敌人，打击其内在自我，造成<color_light_gray>纯粹伤害</color>并<color_yellow>使其无法移动</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_gray>1阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T2.json
msgid "Ethereal Strike"
msgstr "以太打击"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ethereal Strike'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T2.json
msgid ""
"An etherean silhouette emerges out of thin air, immediately attacking the foe that deals <color_light_gray>pure damage</color> and <color_yellow>grasps</color> at them.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_gray>tier 2</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"一个以太虚影凭空出现，立即攻击敌人，造成<color_light_gray>纯粹伤害</color>并<color_yellow>抓住</color>他们。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_gray>2阶</color>法术。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Mana Surge'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T3.json
msgid ""
"<color_yellow>Empowers</color> your body by channeling your mana.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_white>tier 3</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"通过引导法力<color_yellow>强化</color>你的身体。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_white>3阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T4.json
msgid "Dark Burst"
msgstr "黑暗爆发"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dark Burst'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T4.json
msgid ""
"A wave of profane magic bursts out of your body, dealing <color_light_gray>pure damage</color> to the surrounding foes.\n"
"* Foes within a 3 tile radius are <color_yellow>pushed back</color>.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_light_red>tier 4</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"一股亵渎魔法的波浪从你体内爆发，对周围的敌人造成<color_light_gray>纯粹伤害</color>。\n"
"* 3格半径内的敌人被<color_yellow>击退</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_light_red>4阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T5.json
msgid "Megamagic"
msgstr "巨型魔法"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Megamagic'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T5.json
msgid ""
"Obliterates all foes with a devastating wave of profane magic, dealing immensive <color_light_gray>pure damage</color> within a wide cone.\n"
"* 25% chance of <color_yellow>exhaustion</color>, depleting your stamina and weakens yourself for a short period of time.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_red>tier 5</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"用毁灭性的亵渎魔法波浪消灭所有敌人，在宽阔的锥形区域内造成巨大的<color_light_gray>纯粹伤害</color>。\n"
"* 有25%几率<color_yellow>力竭</color>，耗尽你的体力并在短时间内削弱自身。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_red>5阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T5.json
msgid "Dance of the Silhouettes"
msgstr "虚影之舞"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dance of the Silhouettes'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T5.json
msgid ""
"Summons the <color_light_blue>etherean silhouette</color>(s), striding through the world swiftly and are invulnerable to physical hazards.\n"
"* These minions do not harm with brute strength, but casts a basic warlock spell at foe weights from <color_light_gray>tier 1</color> to <color_white>tier 3</color>. After the duration or casting any spell, they vanish."
msgstr ""
"召唤<color_light_blue>以太虚影</color>，它们迅速穿行于世界，对物理危害免疫。\n"
"* 这些仆从不以蛮力造成伤害，而是对敌人施放从<color_light_gray>1阶</color>到<color_white>3阶</color>的基本术士法术。持续时间结束或施放任何法术后，它们会消失。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T6.json
msgid "Dark Pillar"
msgstr "黑暗之柱"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Dark Pillar'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T6.json
msgid ""
"Sky-high pillar of disastrous dark magic engulfs the foe, leaving <color_light_gray>no tracks</color> but a crater.\n"
"* If the foe survives, it is inflicted with <color_yellow>ethereal shock</color>, slowing and dealing a maximum total of <color_light_gray>300 pure damage</color> over 10 seconds.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"灾难性的黑暗魔法形成的冲天之柱吞噬敌人，<color_light_gray>不留痕迹</color>，只留下一个坑洞。\n"
"* 如果敌人幸存，将受到<color_yellow>以太冲击</color>，减速并在10秒内最多造成总计<color_light_gray>300点纯粹伤害</color>。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>6阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T6.json
msgid "Ethereal Enchantment"
msgstr "以太附魔"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Ethereal Enchantment'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T6.json
msgid ""
"You gain an <color_brown>ethereal enchantment</color>, causing your attacks to feel lighter, yet strikes deeper into the inner self of your foe.\n"
"* If worn, your attacks gain <color_light_yellow>20 armor pierce</color> and its cost is reduced by 15.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_magenta>Tier 6</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"你获得一个<color_brown>以太附魔</color>，使你的攻击感觉更轻，却能更深地打击敌人的内在自我。\n"
"* 如果装备，你的攻击获得<color_light_yellow>20点护甲穿透</color>，且其消耗减少15。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_magenta>6阶</color>法术。"

#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T7.json
msgid "Idol: <color_blue>Vex</color>"
msgstr "偶像：<color_blue>维克斯</color>"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Idol: <color_blue>Vex</color>'}
#: .\Modification_Files\Spells\Warlock\v_mana_T7.json
msgid ""
"Calls forth the ancient idol: <color_light_blue>Vex</color>, the etherean calamity. A deity who fulfills your desire for annihilation with its etherean prowess.\n"
"* Once it is successfully summoned, you are affected with <color_yellow>ancient dread</color>, an enormous penalty to intelligence and movement speed.\n"
"* This minion does not harm with brute strength, but casts one from its numerous unique, crowd-control spells.\n"
"\n"
"This is a <color_pink>tier 7</color> spell."
msgstr ""
"召唤远古偶像：<color_light_blue>维克斯</color>，以太灾厄。一位以其以太之力满足你毁灭欲望的神祇。\n"
"* 成功召唤后，你将受到<color_yellow>远古恐惧</color>影响，智力和移动速度大幅降低。\n"
"* 此仆从不以蛮力造成伤害，而是从其众多独特的群体控制法术中施放一种。\n"
"\n"
"这是一个<color_pink>第7阶</color>法术。"
